hadiths[163]{hadithnumber,text}:
3326,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah paak ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida kya to unko sath hath lamba banaya phir farmaya ke ja aur un malaaika ko salam kar, dekhnaa kin lafzon mein wo tumharey salam ka jawab detey hain kyonke wahi tumhara aur tumhari aulad ka tareeqae-salaam hoga. Adam (Alaihissalam) (gaey aur) kaha, Assalaamu-alaikum farishton ne jawab diyaa, Assalaamu-alaikum warahmatullah. unhon-ne warahmatullaah ka jumla badha diya, to jo koi bhi jannat mein dakhil hoga wo Adam (Alaihissalam) ki shakl aur qaamat par dakhil hoga, Adam (Alaihissalam) ke baad insanon mein ab tak qad chhotey hotey rahe. ''"
3327,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''sabse pahlaa giroh jo jannat mein dakhil hoga unki sooratein aisi roshan hongi jaisey chaudahwiin ka chaand roshan hota hai, phir jo log uske baad dakhil hongey wo aasman ke sabse zyada roshan sitaarey ki tarah chamaktey hongey. na to un logon ko peshab ki zarurat hogi na pakhana ki, na wo thookengey na naak se gandagi nikaalegii. unke kanghey soney ke hongey aur unka paseena mashk ki tarah hoga. unki angeethiyon mein khushbu daar Uood jaltaa hoga, ye bahut hi zyada pakeeza khushbu daar Uood hoga. unki beeviyan badi aankhon wali hoorein hongi . sab ki sooratein aik hongi . yani apne walid Adam (Alaihissalam) ke qad w qaamat par saath-saath hath oonchey hongey.''"
3328,"Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala haq baat se nahi sharmaataa , to kya agar aurat ko ehtilam ho to is par bhi ghusl hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' haan basharte ke wo tarii dekh ley.'' Ummul-Momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ko is baat par hansi aa gaee aur farmaney lagein , kya aurat ko bhi ehtilam hota hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(agar aisa nahi hai) to phir bachchey main ( maan ki) mushabihat (similarity) kahan se aati hai''"
3329,"Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Madina tashrif laney ki khabar mili to wo aap ki khidmat mein aaey aur kaha ke main aap se teen chizon ke barey mein poochhoonga. jinhein Nabi ke siwa aur koi nahi janta. qiyamat ki sabse pehli alamat kya hai? wo kon sa khana hai jo sabse pahley jannatiyon ko khaney ke liye diya jaaeyga? aur kis cheez ki wjah se bachcha apne bap ke jaisa hota hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne abhi abhii mujhey aa kar uski khabar di hai. is par Abdullah ne kaha ke malaaika main to yahi to yahudiyon ke dushman hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ki sabse pehli alamat aik aag ki sura mein zahir hogi jo logon ko mashriq se maghrib ki taraf haank ley jaeygi, sabse pahlaa khana jo ahle-jannat ki dawat ke liye pesh kya jaeyga wo machhli ki kalejii par jo tukda takaa rehta hai wo hoga aur bachchey ki mushabihat (similarity) ka jahan tak talluq hai to jab mard aurat ke qareeb jata hai us waqt agar mard ki mani pahal kar jati hai to bachcha usi ki shakl w sura par hota hai. agar aurat ki mani pahal kar jati hai to phir bachcha aurat ki shakl w sura par hota hai.'' (ye sun kar) Abdullaah-bin-Salaam (Raziallahu anhu) bol uthey ''main gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke rasool hain.'' phir arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! yahood intihaa ki jhooti qaum hai. agar aap ke malum karne se pahley mere Islam qabool karne ke barey mein unhein ilm ho gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney mujh par har tarah ki tohmatein dharnii shuru kar dengey. chunanche kuchh Yahudi aaey aur Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ghar ke andar chhup kar baith gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha tum logon mein Abdullaah-bin-Salaam kon sahib hain? sarey Yahudi kehney lagey wo ham mein sabse badey aalim aur sabse badey aalim ke saahib-zaadey hain. ham mein sabse zyada behtar aur ham mein sabse behtar ke sahib zadey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya, agar Abdullah musalman ho jayen to phir tumhara kya khayal hoga? unhon-ne kaha, Allah Taala unhein us se mehfooz rakhey. itney mein Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bahar tashrif laey aur kaha, mein gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad Allah ke sachey rasool hain. ab wo sab unke mutaalliq kehney lagey ke ham mein sabse badtareen aur sabse badtareen ka betaa hai, wahin wo unki burai karne lagey."
3330,agar qaum Bani-Israeel na hoti to gosht na sadaa karta aur agar hawwaa na hotiin to aurat apne shauhar se daghaa na karti.
3331,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aurton ke barey mein meri wasiiyat ka hamesha khayal rakhna, kyonke aurat paslii se paida ki gaee hai. paslii mein bhi sabse zyada tedhaa uper ka hissa hota hai. agar koi shakhs usey bilkul seedhi karne ki koshish karey to anjaame-kaar tod ke rahega aur agar usey wo yoonhii chhod dega to phir hamesha tedhii hi reh jaeygi. to aurton ke barey mein meri nasihat maano, aurton se achchha sulook karo.''"
3332,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan farmaya aur aap sachchon ke sachey they ke insan ki paidaaish uski maa ke pet mein pahley chalis (40) din tak poori ki jati hai. phir wo itney hi dinon tak ( علقة ( yani ghaleez aur jaamid khoon ki sura mein rehta hai. phir itney hi dinon ke liye ( مضغة ( ) gosht ka lothdaa ( ki shakl ikhtiyar kar leta hai. phir (chauthey chille mein) Allah Taala aik farishte ko char baton ka hukm de kar bhejta hai. to wo farishta iske amal, uski muddate-zindagii, rozii aur ye ke wo nek hai ya bad, ko likh leta hai. iske baad usmein Rooh phoonki jati hai. to insan (zindagii bhar) dozkhiyon ke kaam karta rehta hai. aur jab iske aur dozakh ke darmyan sirf aik hath ka fasla reh jata hai to uski taqdeer samney aati hai aur wo jannatiyon ke kaam karne lagta hai aur jannat mein chala jata hai. isi tarah aik shakhs jannatiyon ke kaam karta rehta hai aur jab iske aur jannat ke darmyan sirf aik hath ka fasla reh jata hai to uski taqdeer samney aati hai aur wo dozkhiyon ke kaam shuru kar deta hai aur wo dozakh mein chala jata hai."
3333,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala ne maa ke raham (pet) ke liye aik farishta muqarrar kar diya hai wo farishta arz karta hai, aey rab! ye ( نطفة ( hai, aey rab ye ( مضغة ( hai. aey rab! ye ( علقة ( hai. phir jab Allah Taala usey paida karne ka irada karta hai to farishta poochhta hai aey rab! ye mard hai ya aey rab! ye aurat hai, aey rab! ye bad hai ya nek? uski rozii kya hai? aur muddate-zindagii kitni hai? chunanche usi ke mutabiq maa ke pet hi mein sab kuchh farishta rakh leta hai.''"
3334,"Allah Taala (qiyamat ke din) us shakhs se poochhega jisey dozakh ka sabse halka azab kya gaya hoga. agar duniya mein tumhari koi cheez hoti to kya to us azab se nijat paaney ke liye usey badley mein de sakta tha? wo shakhs kahega ke ji haan is par Allah Taala farmaeyga ke jab to Adam ki peeth mein tha to maine tujh se us se bhi maamooli cheez ka mutalba kya tha (roz zaleel mein) ke mera kisi ko bhi Sharik na thahraanaa, lekin (jab to duniya mein aaya to) usi shirk ka amal ikhtiyar kya."
3335,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab bhi koi insan zulm se qatl kya jata hai to Adam (Alaihissalam) ke sabse pahley betey (Qaabeel) ke naamaae-aa'maal mein bhi us qatl ka gunah likha jata hai. kyonke qatle-naahaq ki bina sabse pahley usi ne qaaim ki thii.''
3336,"imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Lais-bin-Sad ne riwayat kya Yahya-bin-Saeed Ansari se, unse Umra ne aur unse Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ''roohon ke jhund ke jhund alag-alag they. phir wahan jin ruhon mein aapas mein pehchan thi unmein yahan bhi mohabbat hoti hai aur jo wahan ghair thin yahan bhi wo khilaf rehti hain.'' aur Yahya bin Ayub ne bhi us hadis ko riwayat kya, kaha mujh se Yahya-bin-Saeed ne bayan kya, aakhir tak."
3337,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon mein khutba sunaney khadey huey. pahley Allah Taala ki, uski shaan ke mutabiq sana bayan ki, phir dajjal ka zikr farmaya aur farmaya ke main tumhen dajjal ke fitney se daraataa hun aur koi Nabi aisa nahi guzra jisne apni qaum ko us se na daraayaa ho. Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne bhi apni qaum ko us se daraayaa tha. lekin main tumhen iske barey mein aik aisi baat bataataa hun jo kisi Nabi ne bhi apni qaum ko nahi batai thi, tumhen malum hona chahiye ke dajjal kaana hoga aur Allah Taala us aib se paak hai."
3338,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kyon na main tumhen dajjal ke mutaalliq aik aisi baat bata dun jo kisi Nabi ne apni qaum ko ab tak nahi bataaii. wo kaana hoga aur jannat aur jahannam jaisi cheez laaeyga. tu jisey wo jannat kahega dar-haqiqat wahi dozakh hogi aur main tumhen iske fitney se isi tarah daraataa hun, jaisey Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne apni qaum ko daraayaa tha.''"
3339,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' (qiyamat ke din) Nuh (Alaihissalam) baargaahe-Ilaahii mein hazir hongey. Allah Taala malum farmaeyga, kya ( mera paigham ( tum ne pahuncha diya tha? Nuh (Alaihissalam) arz karengey maine tera paigham pahuncha diya tha. aey rabbul-izzat ! ab Allah Taala unki ummat se malum farmaeyga, kya ( Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne) tum tak mera paigham pahuncha diya tha? wo jawab dengey nahi, hamarey paas tera koi Nabi nahi aaya. is par Allah Taala Nuh (Alaihissalam) se malum farmaeyga, uske liye aap ki taraf se koi gawahi bhi de sakta hai? wo arz karengey ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur unki ummat (ke log mere gawah hain) chunanche ham is baat ki shahadat dengey ke Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne Allah Taala ka paigham apni qaum tak pahunchaya tha aur yahi mafhoom Allah ke us irshad ka hai وكذلك جعلناكم أمة وسطا لتكونوا شهداء على الناس''aur isi tarah ham ne tumhen ummate-wast banaya, taake tum logon par gawahi do.'' aur) beech (ke mana darmyani ke hain."
3340,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik dawat mein Sharik they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein dasti ka gosht pesh kya gaya jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bahut marghoob tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us dasti ki haddi ka gosht daanton se nikal kar khaayaa. phir farmaya ke main qiyamat ke din logon ka sardaar hunga . tumhen malum hai ke kis tarah Allah Taala (qiyamat ke din) tamam makhlooq ko aik chatiyal maidan mein jama karega? is tarah ke dekhney wala sab ko aik sath dekh sakega. awaz dene waley ki awaz har jagah suni ja sakey gii aur suraj bilkul qareeb ho jaeyga aik shakhs apne qareeb ke doosrey shakhs se kahega, dekhtey nahi ke sab log kaisi pareshani mein mubtala hain? aur museebat kis had tak pahunch chuki hai? kyon na kisi aisey shakhs ki talash ki jaey jo Allah paak ki bargah mein ham sab ki shafaat ke liye jaey. kuchh logon ka mashwara hoga ke dada Adam (Alaihissalam) uske liye munasib hain. chunanche log unki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey, aey baawaa Adam ! aap insanon ke dada hain. Allah paak ne aapko apne hath se paida kya tha, apni Rooh aap ke andar phoonki thi, malaaika ko hukm diya tha aur unhon-ne aapko sajda kya tha aur jannat mein aapko ( paida karne ke baad) thehraya tha. aap apne rab ke huzoor mein hamari shafaat kar dein. aap khud dekh saktey hain ke ham kis darja uljhan aur pareshani mein mubtala hain. wo farmaaengey ke (gunaah gaaron par) Allah Taala aaj is darja ghazabnaak hai ke kabhi itna ghazabnaak nahi hua tha aur na aainda kabhi hoga aur mujhey pahley hi darakht ( jannat (ke khaney se mana kar chuka tha lekin main is farman ko bajaa laney mein kotahi kar gaya. aaj to mujhey apni hi padi hai (mera nafs-mea nafs) tum log kisi aur ke paas jao. haan, Nuh (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao. chunanche sab log Nuh (Alaihissalam) ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey, aey Nuh (al)! aap (Aadam (Alaihissalam) ke baad) poori zameen par sabse pahley Nabi hain aur Allah Taala ne aapko ''Abd-shukoor'' keh kar pukara hai. aap dekh saktey hain ke aaj ham kaisi museebat w pareshani mein mubtala hain? aap apne rab ke huzoor mein hamari shafaat kar dijiye. wo bhi yahi jawab dengey ke mera rab aaj us darje ghazabnaak hai ke is se pahley kabhi aisa ghazabnaak nahi hua tha aur na kabhi iske baad itna ghazabnaak hoga. aaj to mujhey khud apni hi fikr hai. (mera nafs-mera nafs) tum Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein jao chunanche wo log mere paas aaeingey. mein (unki shafaat ke liye) arsh ke nichey sajdey mein gir padoonga. phir awaz aaeygii, aey Muhammad ! sar uthao aur shafaat karo, tumhari shafaat qabool ki jaeygi. maango tumhen diya jaeyga Muhammad-bin-Ubaidullaah ne bayan kya ke saari hadis mein yad na rakh saka."
3341,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( aayat ) فهل من مدكر mashhoor qirat ke mutabiq tilawat farmai thi.
3342,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere ghar ki chhat kholii gaee. mera qiyam un dinon Makka mein tha. phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) utrey aur mera Sina chaak kya aur usey zamzam ke pani se dhoya. iske baad soney ka aik tasht laey jo hikmat aur eman se labrez tha, usey mere seeney mein undel diya. phir mera hath pakad kar aasman ki taraf lekar chaley, jab aasmaane-duniyaa par pahunchey to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne aasman ke darogha se kaha ke darwaza kholo, puchha ke kon sahib hain? unhon-ne jawab diya ke main Jibraeel, phir puchha ke aap ke sath koi aur bhi hai? jawab diya ke mere sath Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hain, puchha ke unhein laney ke liye aapko bheja gaya tha. jawab diya ke haan, ab darwaza khulaa, jab ham aasman par pahunchey to wahan aik buzurg se mulaqat hui, kuchh insani roohein unke daain taraf thin aur kuchh baain taraf, jab wo daain taraf dekhtey to hans detey aur jab baain taraf dekhtey to ro padtey. unhon-ne kaha khush aamadeed, nek nabii, nek betey ! maine poochha, Jibraeel ! ye sahib kon buzurg hain? to unhon-ne bataya ke ye Adam (Alaihissalam) hain aur ye insani roohein unke daain aur baain taraf thin unki aulad bani-Adam ki roohein thin unke jo daain taraf thin wo jannati thin aur jo baain taraf thin wo dozakhi thin, isi liye jab wo daain taraf dekhtey to muskuratey aur jab baain taraf dekhtey to rotey they, phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) mujhey uper lekar chadhey aur doosrey aasman par aaey, us aasman ke darogha se bhi unhon-ne kaha ke darwaza kholo , unhon-ne bhi isi tarah ke sawalat kiye jo pahley aasman par ho chukey they, phir darwaza khola , Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne tafseel se bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mukhtalif aasmanon par Idrees , Musa , Esa aur Ibrahim ko paya , lekin unhon-ne un anbiya kiram ke maqamat ki koi takhsees nahi ki, sirf itna kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko aasman duniya (pahley aasman par) paya aur Ibrahim ko chhatey par aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir jab Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) , Idrees (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzrey to unhon-ne kaha khush aamadeed, nek nabii, nek bhaaii, maine puchha ke ye kon sahib hain? Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne bataya ke ye Idrees (Alaihissalam) hain, phir main Esa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzraa, unhon-ne bhi kaha khush aamadeed nek nabii, nek bhaaii, maine puchha ye kon sahib hain? to bataya ke Esa (Alaihissalam) . phir Ibrahim ke paas se guzra to unhon-ne farmaya ke khush aamadeed nek Nabi aur nek betey, maine puchha ye kon sahib hain? jawab diya ke ye Ibrahim hain, ibne-Shahab se Zohri ne bayan kya aur mujhey Ayub bin Hazam ne khabar di ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Haiya Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir mujhey uper lekar chadhey aur main itney buland maqam par pahunch gaya jahan se qalam ke likhney ki awaz saaf sunney lagi thi, abu-Bakar-bin-Hazam ne bayan kya aur Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir Allah Taala ne pachaas waqt ki namazein mujh par farz kin. main us fareeze ke sath wapas hua aur jab Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas se guzra to unhon-ne puchha ke aap ki ummat par kya cheez farz ki gaee hai? maine jawab diya ke pachaas waqt ki namazein un par farz hui hain. unhon-ne kaha ke aap apne rab ke paas wapas jayen, kyonke aap ki ummat mein itni namazon ki taqat nahi hai, chunanche main wapas hua aur rabbul-aalameen ke darbar mein pahuncha, iske nateejey mein iska aik hissey kam kar diya gaya, phir main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya aur is martaba bhi unhon-ne kaha ke apne rab ke paas phir se jaayein phir unhon-ne apni tafseelaat ka zikr kya ke rabbul-aalameen ne aik hissey ki phir kami kar di, phir main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya aur unhein khabar ki, unhon-ne kaha ke aap apne rab ke paas phir se jaayein, kyonke aap ki ummat mein uski bhi taqat nahi hai, phir main wapas hua aur apne rab ke paas wapas pahuncha, Allah Taala ne is martaba farma diya ke namazein panch waqt ki kar di gain aur sawab pachaas namazon ka hi baqi rakha gaya, hamara qaul badla nahi karta. phir main Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaya to unhon-ne ab bhi isi par zor diya ke aapko apne rab ke paas phir se jaana chahiye lekin maine kaha ke mujhey Allah paak se baar-baar darkhaast kartey huey ab sharm aati hai. phir Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) mujhey lekar aagey badhey aur sidratul-muntahaa ke paas laey jahan mukhtalif qism ke rang nazar aaey, jinhoney us darakht ko chipa rakha tha main nahi janta ke wo kya they. iske baad mujhey jannat mein dakhil kya gaya to maine dekha ke mautaa ke gunbad baney huey hain aur uski mitti mashk ki tarah khushbu daar thi."
3343,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par) parwaa hawa se meri madad ki gaee aur qaume-aad pachhwaa hawa se halaak kar di gaee thii.''
3344,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( Yaman se) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein kuchh sona bheja to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey char aadmiyon mein taqseem kar diya, Aqra-bin-Habis Hanzali Majaashi'ii, Uena-bin-Badr fazaarii, Zaid Tai banii-nabhaan waley aur Alqama-bin-Ulaasa Aamiri banu- kilaab waale. is par Quraish aur Ansar ke logon ko ghussa aaya aur kehney lagey ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Najad ke badon ko to diya lekin hamein nazar andaz kar diya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main sirf unke dil milaaney ke liye unhein deta hun (kyonke abhi haal hi mein ye log musalman huey hain) phir aik shakhs samney aaya, uski aankhen dhansii hui thin, kalley phooley huey they, peshani bhi uthi hui, dadhi bahut ghanii thi aur sar mundaa hua tha. usne kaha aey Muhammad ! Allah se daro Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar main hi Allah ki nafarmani karunga to phir uski farmaanbardaarii kon karega? Allah Taala ne mujhey poori zameen par dayaanat daar bana kar bheja hai. kya tum mujhey ameen nahi samajhtey? us shakhs ki is gustakhi par aik sahabi ne uske qatl ki ijazat chaahii, mera khayal hai ke ye Khalid-bin Waleed they, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein us se rok diya, phir wo shakhs wahan se chalney laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya us shakhs ki nasl se ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) us shakhs ke baad usi ki qaum se aisey log jhootey musalman paida hongey, jo Quran ki tilawat to karengey, lekin Quran Majeed unke halaq se nichey nahi utreyga, Deen se wo is tarah nikal jaeinge jaisey teer kamaan se nikal jata hai, ye musalmanon ko qatl karengey aur but paraston ko chhod dengey, agar meri zindagi us waqt tak baqi rahe to main unko is tarah qatl karunga jaisey qaume-aad ka (azaabe-Ilaahii se) qatl hua tha ke aik bhi baqi na bachaa."
3345,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap aayat ( فهل من مدكر ( ki tilawat farma rahe they.
3346,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahan tashrif laey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuchh ghabraaey huey they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi, mulk Arab mein us burai ki wjah se barbadi aa jaeygi jiske din qareeb aaney ko hain, aaj yaajooj maajooj ne diwar mein itna suraakh kar diya hai phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne angoothey aur uske qareeb ki ungli se halqa bana kar batlaya . Ummul-Momenin Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine sawal kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya ham iske bawajud halaak kar diye jaeinge ke ham mein nek log bhi maujood hongey ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab fisq w fujoor badh jaeyga (to yaqinan barbadi hogi) ."
3347,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah paak ne Yaajooj-Maajooj ki diwar se itna khol diya hai, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ungliyon se nawwey ka adad bana kar batlaayaa.''"
3348,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala (qiyamat ke din) farmaeyga, aey Adam ! Adam (Alaihissalam) arz karengey mein itaat ke liye hazir hun, muste'ad hun, saari bhalaaiyaan sirf terey hi hath mein hain. Allah Taala farmaeyga, jahannam mein janey walon ko) logon mein se alag ( nikaal lo. Adam (Alaihissalam) arz karengey. aey Allah ! jahannamiyon ki tadaad kitni hai? Allah Taala farmaeyga ke har aik hazaar mein se nau (9) so ninyaanwe. us waqt (ki holnaakii aur wahshat se) bachchey boodhey ho jaeinge aur har haamla aurat apna hamal gira degi. us waqt tum (khauf w dahshat se) logon ko madhoshi ke aalim mein dekhogey, halanke wo behosh na hongey. lekin Allah ka azab bada hi sakht hoga. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! wo aik shakhs ham mein se kon hoga? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen bashaarat ho, wo aik aadmi tum mein se hoga aur aik hazaar dozakhi yaajooj maajooj ki qaum se hongey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, mujhey ummeed hai ke tum (ummate-muslima) tamam jannat walon ke aik tehai hogey. phir ham ne Allahu-akbar kaha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey ummeed hai ke tum tamam jannat walon ke aadhey hogey phir ham ne Allahu-akbar kaha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) mahshar mein) tum log tamam insanon ke muqaabley mein itney hogey jitney kisi safaid bail ke jism par aik siyah baal, ya jitney kisi siyah bail ke jism par aik safaid baal hota hai."
3349,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum log hashr mein nangey paaun, nangey jism aur bin khatna uthaey jao gey.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is aayat ki tilawat ki) كما بدأنا أول خلق نعيده وعدا علينا إنا كنا فاعلين ( '' jaisa ke ham ne paida kya tha pehli martaba, ham aisey hi lautaaeingey. ye hamari taraf se aik wada hai jisko ham pura karke rahengey (sura anbiyaa) aur anbiya mein sabse pahley Ibrahim ko kapda pahnaayaa jaeyga aur mere ashaab mein se kuchh ko jahannam ki taraf ley jaya jaeyga to main pukar uthoonga ke ye to mere ashaab hain, mere ashaab ! lekin mujhey bataya jaeyga ke aap ki wafat ke baad un logon ne phir kufr ikhtiyar kar liya tha. us waqt mein bhi wahi jumla kahunga jo nek bandey (Eisaa (Alaihissalam) ( kahengey ( وكنت عليهم شهيدا ما دمت فيهم‏ ( '' jab tak mein unke sath tha. un par nigraan tha. ''Allah taala ke irshad ( الحكيم ( tak."
3350,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Ibrahim apne walid aazar se qiyamat ke din jab milengey to unke (waalid ke) chehrey par siyaahii aur ghubaar hoga. Ibrahim kahengey ke kya maine aap se nahi kaha tha ke meri mukhalifat na keejiye. wo kahengey ke aaj main aap ki mukhalifat nahi karta. Ibrahim arz karengey ke aey rab! tu ney wada farmaya tha ke mujhey qiyamat ke din ruswa nahi karega. aaj us ruswai se badh kar aur kon si ruswai hogi ke mere walid teri rehmat se sabse zyada door hain. Allah Taala farmaeyga ke maine jannat kaafiron par haram qarar di hai. phir kaha jaeyga ke aey Ibrahim ! tumharey qadmon ke nichey kya cheez hai? wo dekhengey to aik zabah kya hua janwar khoon mein lithdaa hua wahan padaa hoga aur phir iske paon pakad kar usey jahannam mein daal diya jaeyga
3351,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Baitullah mein dakhil huey to usmein Ibrahim aur Maryam (Alaihissalam) ki tasweerein dekhein, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Quraish ko kya ho gayaa? halanke unhein malum hai ke Farishtey kisi aisey ghar mein dakhil nahi hotey jis mein tasweerein rakhi hon, ye Ibrahim ki tasweer hai aur wo bhi paansa phainktey huey."
3352,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab Baitullah mein tasweerein dekhein to andar us waqt tak dakhil na huey jab tak wo mitaa na di gain aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ibrahim aur Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki tasweerein dekhein ke unke hathon mein teer (paansey ke) they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah un par barbadi laey. Allah ki qism un hazraat ne kabhi teer nahi phainkey.''"
3353,"arz kya gaya : ya Rasulullah ! sabse zyada sharif kon hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo sabse zyada parhezgaar ho.'' sahaba ne arz kya ke ham aap se iske mutaalliq nahi poochhtey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''phir Allah ke Nabi Yusuf bin Nabi Allah bin Nabi Allah bin khaleelullaah (sab se zyada sharif hain)'' sahaba ne kaha ke ham iske mutaalliq bhi nahi poochhtey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''achchha Arab ke khandanon ke mutaalliq tum poochhna chahtey ho. suno jo jahiliyat mein sharif they Islam mein bhi wo sharif hain jabke Deen ki samajh unhein aa jaaey.'' abu-Usama aur Motamir ne Ubaidullah se bayan kya, unse Saeed ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
3354,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aaj ki raat mere paas (khuwaab mein) 2 Farishtey (Jibraaiil w Mikaail (al)) aaey. phir ye donon Farishtey mujhey sath lekar aik lambey qad ke buzurg ke paas gaey, wo itney lambey they ke unka sar main nahi dekh paata tha aur ye Ibrahim they.''"
3355,"aap ke samney log dajjal ka tazkira kar rahe they ke uski peshani par likha hua hoga ''kaafir'' ya (yoon likha hua hoga) ''ک  ر'' Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maine ye hadis nahi suni thi. albatta Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik martaba ye hadis bayan farmai ke Ibrahim (ki shakl w waza' malum karne) ke liye tum apne sahib ko dekh saktey ho aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ka badan gathaa hua, gandam goon, aik surkh oont par Sawar they. jiski nakel khajoor ki chhaal ki thi. jaisey mein unhein is waqt bhi dekh raha hun ke wo Allah ki badaai bayan kartey huey wadi mein utar rahe hain."
3356,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ne asii ( 80 ( saal ki umr mein basooley se khatna kya.'' lekin pehli riwayat main ( quddoom ( hai aur ismein ( qudoom ( hai. donon ke mana aik hi hain. yani bisoola (jo badhiyon ka aik mashhoor hathiyar hota hai usey biswa bhi kehtey hain) Shuaib ke sath is hadis ko Abdur-Rehman bin Ishaq ne bhi abu-Zinaad se riwayat kya hai aur Ajlan ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur Muhammad-bin Amr ne abu-Salma se riwayat kya hai, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se."
3357,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ne tauriya teen martaba ke siwa aur kabhi nahi kya.''
3358,"Ibrahim ne teen martaba jhoot bola tha, 2 unmein se khalis izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki raza ke liye they. aik to unka farmana ( bataur tauriya ke) ke ''main bimar hoon'' aur doosra unka ye farmana ke ''balke ye kaam to unke badey ( but ( ne kya hai.'' aur bayan kya ke aik martaba Ibrahim aur Saara (Alaihissalam) aik zaalim badshah ki hudood saltanat se guzar rahe they. badshah ko khabar mili ke yahan aik shakhs aaya hua hai aur uske sath duniya ki aik khoobsurat tareen aurat hai. badshah ne Ibrahim ke paas apna aadmi bhej kar unhein bulwaya aur Saara (Alaihissalam) ke mutaalliq puchha ke ye kon hain? Ibrahim ne farmaya ke ye meri behan hain. phir aap Saara (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaey aur farmaya ke aey saara ! yahan mere aur tumharey siwa aur koi bhi momin nahi hai aur us badshah ne mujh se puchha to maine us se keh diya ke tum meri (denii eitibaar se) behan ho. isliye ab tum koi aisi baat na kehna jis se main jhoota banoon. phir us zaalim ne saara ko bulwaya aur jab wo uske paas gain to usne unki taraf hath badhaanaa chaha lekin fauran hi pakad liya gaya. phir wo kehney laga ke mere liye Allah se dua karo (ke us museebat se nijat de) main ab tumhen koi nuqsan nahi pahunchaaunga . chunanche unhon-ne Allah se dua ki aur wo chhod diya gaya. lekin phir dusri martaba us ne hath badhaya aur us martaba bhi isi tarah pakad liya gaya, balke us se bhi zyada sakht aur phir kehney laga ke Allah se mere liye dua karo, main ab tumhen koi nuqsan nahi pahunchaaunga. Saara (Alaihissalam) ne dua ki aur wo chhod diya gaya. uske baad usne apne kisi khidmat gaar ko bula kar kaha ke tum log mere paas kisi insan ko nahi laey ho, ye to koi sarkash jin hai (jaatey huey) saara (Alaihissalam) ke liye usne Hajra (Alaihissalam) ko khidmat ke liye diya. jab saara aaiin to Ibrahim khadey Namaz padh rahe they. aap ne hath ke ishaare se unka haal poochha. unhon-ne kaha ke Allah Taala ne kaafir ya (ye kaha ke) faajir ke faraib ko usi ke munh par de maara aur Hajra (Alaihissalam) ko khidmat ke liye diya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aey aasmani pani ki aulaad! yani ahal Arab tumhari walida yahi (Haajira (Alaihissalam) ( hain."
3359,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne girgit ko maarney ka hukm diya tha aur farmaya ke usne Ibrahim ki aag par phoonkaa tha.
3360,"jab ye aayat utri ( الذين آمنوا ولم يلبسوا إيمانهم بظلم‏ ( ''jo log eman laey aur apne eman mein kisi qism ke zulm ki milawat na ki.'' to ham ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham mein aisa kon hoga jisne apni jaan par zulm na kya hoga? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke waqia wo nahi jo tum samajhtey ho. jisne apne eman ke sath zulm ki milawat na ki. (mein zulm se muraad) shirk hai. kya tum ne luqman (Alaihissalam) ki apne betey ko ye nasihat nahi suni ke ''aey betey! Allah ke sath Sharik na karnaa, beshak shirk bahut hi bada zulm hai.''"
3361,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik martaba gosht pesh kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala qiyamat ke din awwaleen w aakhareen ko aik hamwaar aur wasee maidan mein jama karega, is tarah ke pukarney wala sab ko apni baat suna sakega aur dekhney wala sab ko aik sath dekh sakega (kyonke ye maidan hamwaar hoga, zameen ki tarah gol na hoga) aur logon se suraj bilkul qareeb ho jaeyga phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shafaat ka zikr kya ke log Ibrahim ki khidmat mein hazir hongey aur arz karengey ke aap poori zameen par Allah ke Nabi aur khaleel hain. hamarey liye apne rab ke huzoor mein shafaat keejiye, phir unhein apne jhoot (tauriya) yad aa jaaenge aur kahengey ke aaj to mujhey apni hi fikr hai. tum log Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas jao. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us hadis ko riwayat kya hai."
3362,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki walida (Haajira (Alaihissalam) ( par raham karey, agar unhon-ne jaldi na ki hoti (aur zamzam ke pani ke gird munder na banaatiin) to aaj wo aik bahtaa hua chashma hotaa.''"
3363,"main aur Usman bin-abu-Sulaimaan donon Saeed-bin-Jubair ke paas baithey huey they, itney mein unhon-ne kaha ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se ye hadis is tarah bayan nahi ki balke yun kaha ke Ibrahim apne betey Ismail aur unki walida Hajra (Alaihissalam) Ismail (Alaihissalam) ko lekar Makka ki sar zameen ki taraf aaey. Hajra (Alaihissalam) Ismail (Alaihissalam) ko doodh pilaatii thin. unke sath aik puraanii mashk thi. Ibne-Abbas ne us hadis ko marfooa' nahi kya."
3364,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, aurton mein kamar-patta baandhney ka riwaaj Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki walida ( Hajra (Alaihissalam) ( se chala hai. sabse pahley unhon-ne kamar-patta isliye baandha tha taake Saara (Alaihissalam) unka suraagh na paaein (wo jald bhag jayen ( phir unhein aur unke betey Ismail ko Ibrahim ( (Alaihissalam) ( sath lekar Makka mein aaey, us waqt abhi wo Ismail (Alaihissalam) ko doodh pilaatii thin. Ibrahim ne donon ko Kaba ke paas aik badey darakht ke paas bitha diya jo us jagah tha jahan ab zamzam hai. masjid ki buland taraf mein. un dinon Makka mein koi insan nahi tha. isliye wahan pani nahi tha. Ibrahim ne un donon ko wahin chhod diya aur unke liye aik chamdey ke thailey mein khajoor aur aik mashk mein pani rakh diya. phir Ibrahim (apne ghar ke liye) rawaana huey. us waqt Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki walida unke peechhey-peechhey aaein aur kaha ke aey Ibrahim ! us khushk jangal mein jahan koi bhi aadmi aur koi bhi cheez maujood nahi, aap hamein chhod kar kahan ja rahe hain? unhon-ne kai baar is baat ko dohraya lekin Ibrahim unki taraf dekhtey nahi they. aakhir Hajra (Alaihissalam) ne puchha kya Allah Taala ne aapko iska hukm diya hai? Ibrahim ne farmaya ke haan. is par Hajra (Alaihissalam) bol uthiin ke phir Allah Taala hamari hifazat karega, wo ham ko halaak nahi karega. chunanche wo wapas aa gain aur Ibrahim rawaana ho gaey. jab wo saniya pahaadii par pahunchey jahan se wo dikhai nahi detey they, to idhar rukh kya, jahan ab Kaba hai) jahan par Hajra aur Ismail (Alaihissalam) ko chhod kar aaey they) phir aap ne donon hath utha kar ye dua ki ke aey mere rab! maine apni aulad ko us bey-aabo-daana maidan main teri hurmat waley ghar ke paas thehraya hai (sura Ibrahim يشكرون‏) tak. idhar Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki walida unko doodh pilaaney lagiin aur khud pani peeney lagiin. aakhir jab mashk ka Sara pani khatm ho gaya to wo piyaasii rehney lagiin aur unke lakhte-jigar bhi piyaasey rehney lagey. wo ab dekh rahi thin ke samney unka betaa (piyaas ki shiddat se) pecho-taab kha raha hai ya (kaha ke) zameen par lot raha hai. wo wahan se hat gain kyonke is haalat mein bachchey ko dekhney se unka dil be-chain hota tha. Safa pahaadii wahan se nazdeek tar thi. wo (paanii ki talash mein) is par chadh gain aur wadi ki taraf rukh karke dekhney lagiin ke kahin koi insan nazar aaey lekin koi insan nazar nahi aaya, wo Safa se utar gain aur jab wadi mein pahunchiin to apna daman utha liya (taake daudtey waqt na uljhein) aur kisi pareshan haal ki tarah daudney lagiin phir wadi se nikal kar Marwa pahaadii par aaiin aur is par khadi ho kar dekhney lagiin ke kahin koi insan nazar aaey lekin koi nazar nahi aaya. is tarah unhon-ne saat (7) chakkar lagaey. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (Safaa aur Marwa ke darmyaan) logon ke liye daudnaa usi wjah se lazim hua. (saatween martaba) jab wo Marwa par chadhiin to unhein aik awaz sunai di, unhon-ne kaha, khamosh ! ye khud apne hi se wo keh rahi thin aur phir awaz ki taraf unhon-ne kaan laga diye. awaz ab bhi sunai de rahi thi phir unhon-ne kaha ke tumhari awaz maine suni. agar tum meri koi madad kar saktey ho to karo. kya dekhti hain ke jahan ab zamzam (ka kunwaan ( hai, wahin aik farishta maujood hai. Farishtey ne apni eidii se zameen mein garhaa kar diya, ya ye kaha ke apne bazu se, jis se wahan pani ubal aaya. Hajra ne usey hauz ki shakl mein bana diya aur apne hath se is tarah kar diya (taake pani bahney na paaey (aur chullu pani apne mishkeeza mein dalney lagiin. jab wo bhar chukiin to wahan se chashma phir ubal padaa . Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ! Umme- Ismail par raham karey, agar zamzam ko unhon-ne yun hi chhod diya hota ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chullu mishkeeza na bharaa hota to zamzam aik bahte huey chashmey ki sura mein hota. bayan kya ke phir Hajra (Alaihissalam) ne khud bhi wo pani piyaa aur apne betey ko bhi pilaayaa. iske baad unse Farishtey ne kaha ke apne barbad honey ka khof hargiz na karna kyonke yahin Allah ka ghar hoga, jisey ye bachcha aur uska bap tameer karengey aur Allah apne bandon ko zaaye nahi karta, ab jahan Baitullah hai, us waqt wahan teeley ki tarah zameen uthi hui thi. sailaab ka dhara aata aur uske daaein baaein se zameen kaat kar ley jata. is tarah wahan ke din w raat guzartey rahe aur aakhir aik din qabila Jurham ke kuchh log wahan se guzrey ya (aap ne ye farmaya ke) qabila Jurham ke chand gharaaney maqam kadaa (Makka ka oopri hissey (ke rastey se guzar kar Makka ke nashebii ilaaqey mein unhon-ne padao kya ( qareeb hi ( unhon-ne mandlaatey huey kuchh parindey dekhey , un logon ne kaha ke ye parinda pani par mandlaa raha hai. halanke us se pahley jab bhi ham us maidan se guzrey hain yahan pani ka naam w nishan bhi na tha. aakhir unhon-ne apna aik aadmi ya 2 aadmi bhejey. wahan unhon-ne waqei pani paya chunanche unhon-ne wapas aa kar pani ki itlaa di. ab ye sab log yahan aaey. rawi ne bayan kya ke Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki walida us waqt pani par hi baithi hui thin. un logon ne kaha ke kya aap hamein apne padaus mein padao dalney ki ijazat dengii. Hajra (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke haan, lekin is shart ke sath ke pani par tumhara koi haq nahi hoga. unhon-ne usey taslim kar liya. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ab umme-Ismaaeel ko padosi mil gaey. insanon ki maujoodgii unke liye dil-jamaaii ka baais hui. un logon ne khud bhi yahan qiyam kya aur apne qabeeley ke doosrey logon ko bhi bulwa liya aur wo sab log bhi yahin aa kar thahar gaey. is tarah yahan unke kai gharaaney aa kar abad ho gaey aur bachcha (Ismail (Alaihissalam) Jurham ke bachchon mein) jawan hua aur unse arabii seekh li. jawaanii mein Ismail (Alaihissalam) aisey khoobsurat they ke aap par sab ki nazrein uthtii thin aur sabse zyada aap bhaley lagtey they. chunanche Jurham walon ne aap ki apne qabeeley ki aik ladki se shadi kar di. phir Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki walida ( Hajra (Alaihissalam) (ka intiqal ho gaya) . Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki shadi ke baad Ibrahim yahan apne chhodey huey khandan ko dekhney aaey. Ismail (Alaihissalam) ghar par nahi they. isliye aap ne unki biwi se Ismail (Alaihissalam) ke mutaalliq poochha. unhon-ne bataya ke rozii ki talash mein kahin gaey hain. phir aap ne unse unki rozi-roti wghaira ke mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke haalat achi nahi hai, badi tangi se guzar oqaat hoti hai. is tarah unhon-ne shikayat ki. Ibrahim ne unse farmaya ke jab tumhara shauhar aaey to unse mera salam kehna aur ye bhi kehna ke wo apne darwazey ki chaukhat badal daalein. phir jab Ismail (Alaihissalam) wapas tashrif laey to jaisey unhon-ne kuchh unsiyat si mehsus ki aur malum farmaya, kya koi sahib yahan aaey they? unki biwi ne bataya ke yahan aik buzurg is-is shakl ke yahan aaey they aur aap ke barey mein poochh rahe they, maine unhein bataya (ke aap bahar gaey huey hain) phir unhon-ne puchha ke tumhari guzar oqaat ka kya haal hai? to maine unse kaha ke hamari guzar oqaat badi tangi se hoti hai. Ismail (Alaihissalam) ne malum kya ke unhon-ne tumhen kuchh nasihat bhi ki thi? unki biwi ne bataya ke haan mujh se unhon-ne kaha tha ke aapko salam keh dun aur wo ye bhi keh gaey hain ke aap apne darwazey ki chaukhat badal dein. Ismail (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke wo buzurg mere walid they aur mujhey ye hukm de gaey hain ke main tumhen juda kar dun, ab tum apne ghar ja sakti ho. chunanche Ismail (Alaihissalam) ne unhein talaaq de di aur banii-Jurham hi mein aik dusri aurat se shadi kar li. jab tak Allah Taala ko manzoor raha, Ibrahim unke yahan nahi aaey. phir jab kuchh dinon ke baad wo tashrif laey to is martaba bhi Ismail (Alaihissalam) apne ghar par maujood nahi they. aap unki biwi ke yahan gaey aur unse Ismail (Alaihissalam) ke barey mein poochha. unhon-ne bataya ke hamarey liye rozii talash karne gaey hain. Ibrahim ne puchha tum logon ka haal kaisa hai? aap ne unki guzar Basar aur doosrey halaat ke mutaalliq poochha, unhon-ne bataya ke hamara haal bahut achchha hai, badi faraakhii hai, unhon-ne uske liye Allah ki tareef w sana ki. Ibrahim ne malum farmaya ke tum log khaatey kya ho? unhon-ne bataya ke gosht! aap ne malum kya farmaya ke peetey kya ho? bataya ke pani ! Ibrahim ne unke liye dua ki, aey Allah unke gosht aur pani mein barkat nazil farmaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un dinon unhein anaaj muyassar nahi tha. agar anaaj bhi unke khaney mein shamil hota to zaroor aap usmein bhi barkat ki dua kartey. sirf gosht aur pani ki khuraak mein hamesha guzaara karna Makka ke siwa aur kisi zameen par bhi muwafiq nahi padta . Ibrahim ne ( jatey huey) us se farmaya ke jab tumharey shauhar wapas aa jayen to unse mera salam kehna aur unse keh dena ke wo apne darwazey ki chaukhat baqi rakhein. jab Ismail (Alaihissalam) tashrif laey to puchha ke kya yahan koi aaya tha? unhon-ne bataya ke ji haan aik buzurg , badi achi shakl w sura ke aaey they. biwi ne aaney waley buzurg ki tareef ki phir unhon-ne mujh se aap ke mutaalliq puchha (ke kahan hain?) aur maine bata diya, phir unhon-ne puchha ke tumhari guzar Basar ka kya haal hai. to maine bataya ke ham achi haalat mein hain. Ismail (Alaihissalam) ne malum farmaya ke kya unhon-ne tumhen koi wasiiyat bhi ki thi? unhon-ne kaha ji haan, unhon-ne aapko salam kaha tha aur hukm diya tha ke apne darwazey ki chaukhat ko baqi rakhein. Ismail (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke ye buzurg mere walid they, chaukhat tum ho aur aap mujhey hukm de gaey hain ke main tumhen apne sath rakhoon . phir jitney dinon Allah Taala ko manzoor raha, ke baad Ibrahim unke yahan tashrif laey to dekha ke Ismail zamzam ke qareeb aik badey darakht ke saaey main ( jahan Ibrahim unhein chhod gaey they) apne teer bana rahe hain. jab Ismail (Alaihissalam) ne Ibrahim ko dekha to unki taraf khadey hogey aur jis tarah aik bap apne betey ke sath aur betaa apne bap ke sath mohabbat karta hai wahi tarze-amal un donon ne bhi aik doosrey ke sath ikhtiyar kya. phir Ibrahim ne farmaya, Ismail Allah ne mujhey aik hukm diya hai. Ismail (Alaihissalam) ne arz kya, aap ke rab ne jo hukm aapko diya hai aap usey zaroor pura karein. unhon-ne farmaya aur tum bhi meri madad kar sakogey? arz kya ke main aap ki madad karunga . farmaya ke Allah Taala ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke main usi maqam par Allah ka aik ghar banaun aur aap ne aik aur oonchey teeley ki taraf ishara kya ke iske charon taraf ! kaha ke us waqt un donon ne Baitullah ki buniyad par Imaarat ki tameer shuru ki. Ismail (Alaihissalam) patthar utha utha kar latey aur Ibrahim tameer kartey jatey they. jab diwarein buland ho gain to Ismail ye patthar laey aur Ibrahim ke liye usey rakh diya. ab Ibrahim us patthar par khadey ho kar tameer karne lagey. Ismail (Alaihissalam) patthar detey jatey they aur ye donon ye dua padhtey jatey they. hamarey rab! hamari ye khidmat to qabool kar beshak to bada sunney wala aur jaanney wala hai. farmaya ke ye donon tameer kartey rahe aur Baitullah ke charon taraf ghoom ghoom kar ye dua padhtey rahe. ''aey hamarey rab! hamari taraf se ye khidmat qabool farmaa. beshak to bada sunney wala bahut jaanney wala hai.''"
3365,"Ibrahim aur unki biwi (Saara (Alaihissalam) (ke darmyan jo kuchh jhagdaa hona tha jab wo hua to aap Ismail (Alaihissalam) aur unki walida ( Hajra (Alaihissalam) ( ko lekar nikley, unke sath aik mishkeeza tha. jis mein pani tha, Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki walida usi mishkeeze ka pani peeti rahiin aur apna doodh apne bachchey ko pilaatii rahiin. jab Ibrahim Makka pahunchey to unhein aik badey darakht ke paas thehra kar apne ghar wapas janey lagey. Ismail (Alaihissalam) ki walida unke peechhey-peechhey aaiin. jab maqam kadaa par pahunchey to unhon-ne peechhey se awaz di ke aey Ibrahim (al)! hamein kis par chhod kar ja rahe hain? unhon-ne farmaya ke Allah par! Hajra (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke phir main Allah par khush hun. bayan kya ke phir Hajra apni jagah par wapas chali aaiin aur usi mishkeezey se pani peeti rahiin aur apna doodh apne bachchey ko pilaatii rahiin jab pani khatm ho gaya to unhon-ne sochaa ke idhar-udhar dekhnaa chaahiye, mumkin hai ke koi aadmi nazar aa jaey. rawi ne bayan kya ke yahi soch kar wo Safa (pahaadii) par chadh gain aur charon taraf dekha ke shayad koi nazar aa jaey lekin koi nazar na aaya. phir jab wadi mein utriin to daud kar Marwa tak aaein. isi tarah kai chakkar lagaaey, phir sochaa ke chalun zara bachchey ko to dekhun kis haalat mein hai. chunanche aaiin aur dekha to bachcha usi haalat mein tha (jaisey takleef ke maarey) maut ke liye tadap raha ho. ye haal dekh kar unse sabr na ho sakaa, sochaa chalun dobara dekhun mumkin hai ke koi aadmi nazar aa jaey, aaiin aur Safa pahaad par chadh gain aur charon taraf nazar pher pher kar dekhti rahiin lekin koi nazar na aaya. is tarah Hajra (Alaihissalam) ne saat (7) chakkar lagaey phir sochaa , chalun dekhun bachcha kis haalat mein hai? usi waqt unhein aik awaz sunai di. unhon-ne ( awaz se mukhaatab ho kar) kaha ke agar tumharey paas koi bhalai hai to meri madad karo. wahan Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) maujood they. unhon-ne apni eidii se yun kya (ishaara karke bataayaa) aur zameen eidii se khodi. rawi ne bayan kya ke is amal ke nateejey mein wahan se pani phoot padaa. umme-Ismaaeel dariin. (kahiin ye pani ghayab na ho jaey) phir wo zameen khodney lagein . rawi ne bayan kya ke abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar wo pani ko yun hi rehney detiin to pani zameen par bahtaa rahtaa. gharaz Hajra (Alaihissalam) zamzam ka pani peeti rahiin aur apna doodh apne bachchey ko pilaatii rahiin. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke iske baad qabila Jurham ke kuchh log wadi ke nichley hissey se guzrey. unhein wahan parindey nazar aaey. unhein ye kuchh khilaafe-aadat malum hua. unhon-ne aapas mein kaha ke parinda to sirf pani hi par (is tarah) mandlaa sakta hai. un logon ne apna aadmi wahan bhejaa. usne ja kar dekha to waqei wahan pani maujood tha. us ne aa kar apne qabeeley walon ko khabar di to ye sab log yahan aagey aur kaha ke aey umme-Ismaaeel! kya hamein apne sath rehney ki ya (ye kaha ke) apne sath qiyam karne ki ijazat dengii? phir unke betey (Ismail (al)) baligh huey aur qabila Jurham hi ki aik ladki se unka nikah ho gaya. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Ibrahim ko khayal aaya aur unhon-ne apni ahliya (Saara (al)) se farmaya ke main jin logon ko (Makka mein) chhod aaya tha unki khabar leney jaaunga. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Ibrahim Makka tashrif laey aur salam karke malum farmaya ke Ismail kahan hain? unki biwi ne bataya ke shikar ke liye gaey. unhon-ne farmaya ke jab wo aaein to unse kehna ke apne darwazey ki chaukhat badal daalein. jab Ismail (Alaihissalam) aaey to unki biwi ne waaqie ki itlaa di. Ismail (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke tumhiin ho (jisey badalney ke liye Ibrahim keh gaey hain) ab tum apne ghar ja sakti ho. bayan kya ke phir aik muddat ke baad dobara Ibrahim ko khayal hua aur unhon-ne apni biwi se farmaya ke main jin logon ko chhod aaya hun unhein dekhney jaaunga . rawi ne bayan kya ke Ibrahim tashrif laey aur malum farmaya ke Ismail kahan hain? unki biwi ne bataya ke shikar ke liye gaey hain. unhon-ne ye bhi kaha ke aap thahariye aur khana tanaawul farma lijiye. Ibrahim ne malum farmaya ke tum log khaatey peetey kya ho? unhon-ne bataya ke gosht khaatey hain aur pani peetey hain. aap ne dua ki ke aey Allah ! unke khaney aur unke pani mein barkat nazil farmaa. bayan kya ke abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Ibrahim ki is dua ki barkat ab tak chali aa rahi hai. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir ( teesri baar ( Ibrahim ko aik muddat ke baad khayal hua aur apni ahliya se unhon-ne kaha ke jinko mein chhod aaya hun unki khabar leney Makka jaaunga. chunanche aap tashrif laey aur is martaba Ismail (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat hui, jo zamzam ke peechhey apne teer theek kar rahe they. Ibrahim ne farmaya, aey Ismaaeel! tumharey rab ne mujhey hukm diya hai ke main yahan uska aik ghar banaaun, betey ne arz kya ke phir aap apne rab ka hukm bajaa laaiye. unhon-ne farmaya aur mujhey ye bhi hukm diya hai ke tum is kaam mein meri madad karo. arz kya ke main uske liye taiyaar hun. ya isi qism ke aur alfaz ada kiye. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir donon bap betey uthey. Ibrahim diwarein uthatey they aur Ismail (Alaihissalam) unhein patthar laa-laa kar detey they aur donon ye dua kartey jatey they. aey hamarey rab! hamari taraf se ye khidmat qabool kar. beshak to bada sunney waalaa, bahut jaanney wala hai. rawi ne bayan kya ke aakhir jab diwar buland ho gaee aur buzurg (Ibraaheem (al)) ko patthar (diiwaar par) rakhney mein dushwari hui to wo maqam (Ibraaheem (al)) ke patthar par khadey huey aur Ismail (Alaihissalam) unko patthar utha utha kar detey jatey aur un hazraat ki zaban par ye dua jari thi. ''aey hamarey rab! hamari taraf se usey qabool farma ley. beshak to bada sunney wala bahut jaanney wala hai.''"
3366,"maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! sabse pahley poori zameen par kon si masjid bani hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke masjide-Haraam. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir maine arz kya aur aur uske ba'd? farmaya ke masjide-Aqsaa (baitul-maqdis) maine arz kya, un donon ki tameer ke darmyan kitna fasla raha hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke chalis (40) saal. phir farmaya ab jahan bhi tujh ko Namaz ka waqt ho jaey wahan Namaz padh ley. badi fazeelat Namaz padhna hai."
3367,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud pahaad ko dekh kar farmaya ke ye pahaad ham se mohabbat rakhta hai aur ham us se mohabbat rakhtey hain. aey Allah ! Ibrahim ne Makka Mukarrama ko hurmat wala Shahar qarar diya tha aur main Madina ke 2 pathreeley ilaaqey ke darmyani ilaaqey ke hissey ko hurmat wala qarar deta hun. is hadis ko Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai.
3368,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tumhein malum nahi ke jab tumhari qaum ne Kaba ki (naii) tameer ki to Kaba ki Ibraaheemii buniyad ko chhod diyaa.'' maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! phir aap Ibraaheemii buniyaadon ke mutabiq dobara uski tameer kyon nahi kar detey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tumhari qaum ka zamana kufr se qareeb na hota (to main aisa hi kartaa) Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jabke ye hadis Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai to mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un donon ruknon ke, jo hajre-Aswad ke qareeb hain, bosa leney ko sirf isi wjah se chhoda tha ke Baitullah Ibrahim ki buniyad par nahi bana hai (ye donon rukn aagey hat gaey hain) Ismaaeel-bin-abii-Ovais ne is hadis mein Abdullaah-bin-Muhammad-bin abi-Bakr kahaa."
3369,sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham aap par kis tarah durood bheja karein? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yun kaha karo اللهم صل على محمد وأزواجه وذريته ، Mina padhi. كما صليت على آل إبراهيم ، Mina padhi. وبارك على محمد وأزواجه وذريته ، Mina padhi. كما باركت على آل إبراهيم ، Mina padhi. إنك حميد مجيد‏''aey Allah ! rehmat nazil farma Muhammad par aur unki beeviyon par aur unki aulad par jaisa ke tu ney rehmat nazil farmai Ibrahim par aur apni barkat nazil farma Muhammad par aur unki beeviyon aur aulad par jaisa ke tu ney barkat nazil farmai aal Ibrahim par. beshak to intihai khoobiyon wala aur azmat wala hai.''
3370,aik martaba Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) se meri mulaqat hui to unhon-ne kaha kyon na tumhen (hadees ka ( aik tohfa pahuncha dun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha. maine arz kya ji haan mujhey ye tohfa zaroor inayat farmaiye. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha tha ya Rasulullah! ham aap par aur aap ke ahale-bait par kis tarah durood bheja karein? Allah Taala ne salam bhejney ka tariqa to hamein khud hi sikhaa diya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yun kaha karo اللهم صل على محمد ، Mina padhi. وعلى آل محمد ، Mina padhi. كما صليت على إبراهيم وعلى آل إبراهيم ، Mina padhi. إنك حميد مجيد ، Mina padhi. اللهم بارك على محمد ، Mina padhi. وعلى آل محمد ، Mina padhi. كما باركت على إبراهيم ، Mina padhi. وعلى آل إبراهيم ، Mina padhi. إنك حميد مجيد ''aey Allah ! apni rehmat nazil farma Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aur aal Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jaisa ke tu ney apni rehmat nazil farmai Ibrahim par aur aal Ibrahim par. beshak to badi khoobiyon wala aur buzurgi wala hai. aey Allah ! barkat nazil farma Muhammad par aur aal Muhammad par jaisa ke tu ney barkat nazil farmai Ibrahim par aur aal Ibrahim par. beshak to badi khoobiyon wala aur badi azmat wala hai.
3371,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hasan w Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye panah talab kya kartey they aur farmatey they ke tumharey buzurg dada (Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ( bhi in kalimaat ke zariey Allah ki panah Ismail aur Ishaq (Alaihissalam) ke liye maanga kartey they. أعوذ بكلمات الله التامة من كل شيطان وهامة ، Mina padhi. ومن كل عين لامة ''main panah mangta hun Allah ke poorey-poorey kalimaat ke zariey har aik shaitan se aur har zahreeley janwar se aur har nuqsan pahunchaney wali nazare-bd se.''
3372,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ham Ibrahim ke muqaabley mein shak karne ke zyada mustahiq hain jabke unhon-ne kaha tha ke mere rab! mujhey dikhaa ke to mardon ko kis tarah zinda karta hai. Allah Taala ne farmaya ''kahaa kya tum eman nahi laaey, unhon-ne arz kya ke kyon nahi, lekin ye sirf isliye taake mere dil ko aur zyada itminan ho jaaey.'' aur Allah loot (Alaihissalam) par raham karke wo zabardast rukn (yani Allah Taala ( ki panah letey they aur agar main itni muddat tak qaid-khaaney mein rehta jitni muddat tak Yusuf (Alaihissalam) rahe they, to main bulaney waley ke baat zaroor maan letaa.''"
3373,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabila Aslam ki aik jamat se guzrey jo teer andazi mein muqaabla kar rahi thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey banu-Ismaaeel! teer-andaazii kiye jao kyonke tumharey buzurg dada bhi teerandaaz they aur main banu- falan ke sath hoon.'' rawi ne bayan kya ke ye suntey hi doosrey fareeq ne teer andazi band kar di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kya baat hui, tum log teer kyon nahi chalaatey?'' unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! jab aap fareeq muqabil ke sath ho gaey to ab ham kis tarah teer chala saktey hain. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''muqaabla jari rakho, main tum sab ke sath hoon.''"
3374,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : sabse zyada sharif kon hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo sabse zyada muttaqii ho, wo sabse zyada sharif hai. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hamarey sawal ka maqsad ye nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' phir sabse zyada sharif Yusuf Nabi Allah bin Nabi Allah ( Yaqoob (bin Nabi Allah ( Ishaq (bin khaleelullaah (Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ( they.'' sahaba ne arz kya : hamarey sawal ka maqsad ye bhi nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kya tum log Arab ke shareefon ke barey mein poochhna chahtey ho?'' sahaba ne arz kya ke ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''phir jahiliyat mein jo log sharif aur achchhey aadaat w akhlaq ke they wo Islam laney ke baad bhi sharif aur achchhey samjhey jaeinge jabke wo Deen ki samajh bhi hasil karein.''"
3375,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala loot (Alaihissalam) ki maghfirat farmaai ke wo zabardast rukn (yani Allah ( ki panah mein gaey they.''
3376,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( فهل من مدكر ( padha tha.
3377,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ( khutbe ke doran (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qaum ka zikr kya jinhonney ontni ko zabah kar diya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (Allah ki qism bheji hui) us (oontnii) ko zabah karne wala qaum ka aik bahut hi baa-izzat aadmi (qeedaar naamii) tha, jaisey hamarey zamaney mein abu-Zama'a (Aswad-bin-Muttalib) hai."
3378,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab Hijr (Samood ki bastii) mein jange-Tabook ke liye jatey huey padao kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm farmaya ke yahan ke kunon ka pani na peenaa aur na apne bartanon mein sath lenaa. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke hamney to us se apna aata bhi goondh liya hai aur pani apne bartanon mein bhi rakh liya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke gundhaa hua aata phenk diya jaey aur Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kya hai ke jisne aata us pani se goondh liya ho (wo usey phenk de).
3379,sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Samood ki basti hijr mein padao kya to wahan ke kunon ka pani apne bartanon mein bhar liya aur aata bhi us pani se goondh liya. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hukm diya ke jo pani unhon-ne apne bartanon mein bhar liya hai usey undel dein aur gandhaa hua aata janwaron ko khilaa dein. iske bajaey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ye hukm diya ke us kuwein se pani lein jis se Saleh (Alaihissalam) ki ontni pani piyaa karti thi.
3380,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab maqam hijr se guzrey to farmaya ''un logon ki basti mein jinhoney zulm kya tha na dakhil ho, lekin is sura mein ke tum rotey huey ho. kahin aisa na ho ke tum par wahi azab aa jaey jo un par aaya tha.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni chadar chehre Mubarak par daal li. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt kajaawey par tashrif rakhtey they."
3381,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab tumhen un logon ki basti se guzarna padey jinhonney apni jaanon par zulm kya tha to rotey huey guzro. kahin tumhen bhi wo azab aa na pakdey jis mein ye zaalim log giraftaar kiye gaey they.''
3382,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''shareef bin sharif bin sharif bin shareef, Yusuf bin Yaqoob bin Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) they.''"
3383,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke sabse zyada sharif aadmi kon hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo Allah ka khof zyada rakhta ho.'' sahaba ne arz kya ke hamarey sawal ka maqsad ye nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir sabse zyada sharif Allah ke Nabi Yusuf bin Nabi Allah bin Nabi Allah bin khaleelullaah hain. sahaba ne arz kya ke hamarey sawal ka maqsad ye bhi nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log Arab ke khaanwaadon ke barey mein poochhna chahtey ho. dekho! logon ki misal kanon (mines) ki si hai (kisi kaan mein se achchha maal nikalta hai kisi mein se buraa) jo log tum mein se zamana jahiliyat mein sharif aur behtar akhlaq ke they wahi Islam ke baad bhi achchhey aur sharif hain basharte ke wo Deen ki samajh hasil karein.
3384,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (marzul-maut mein) unse farmaya ''abu-Bakar se kaho ke logon ko Namaz padhaaein, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya ke wo bahut narm dil hain, aap ki jagah jab khadey hongey to un par ronaa taarii ho jaeyga Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dobara yahi hukm diya. lekin unhon-ne bhi dobara yahi uzr bayan kya, Shoba ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri ya chothi martaba farmaya ke tum to Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ki sath waaliyaan ho. ( zahir mein kuchh baton mein kuchh) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaho Namaz padhaaein.''"
3385,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bimar padey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abu-Bakar se kaho ke logon ko Namaz padhaaein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bahut hi zyada narm dil insan hain lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dobara yahi hukm farmaya aur unhon-ne bhi wahi uzr dohraayaa. aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unse kaho Namaz padhaaein. tum to Yusuf ki sath waaliyaan ho. (zaahir kuchh baatin kuchh) chunanche Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zindagi mein imamat ki aur Husain-bin-Ali-Jau'fii ne Zayda se (رجل رقيق‏) ke alfaz naql kiye ke Abu-Bakar narm dil aadmi hain.
3386,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmaaii اللهم أنج Ayash بن أبي ربيعة ، Mina padhi. اللهم أنج سلمة بن هشام ، Mina padhi. اللهم أنج الوليد بن الوليد اللهم أنج المستضعفين من المؤمنين ، Mina padhi. اللهم اشدد وطأتك على مضر ، Mina padhi. اللهم اجعلها سنين كسني يوسف''aey Allah ! Ayaash-bin-abii-Rabee'a ko nijat de, aey Allaah! Salma-bin-Hishaam ko nijat de, aey Allah ! Waleed-bin-Waleed ko nijat de, aey Allah tamam zaeef aur kamzor musalmanon ko nijat de. aey Allaah! qabila Muzar ko sakht giraft mein pakad ley. aey Allah ! Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamaney ki si qahat saalii un ( zaalimon ( par nazil farmaa.''"
3387,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala loot (Alaihissalam) par raham farmaai ke wo zabardast rukn (yani Allah ta'alaa) ki panah letey they aur agar main itni muddat tak qaid rehta jitni Yusuf (Alaihissalam) rahe they aur phir mere paas (baadshaah ka aadmii) bulaney ke liye aata to main fauran uske sath chala jaataa.''
3388,"maine Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki walida umme-Roomaan (Raziallahu anhu) se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke barey mein jo bohtan ghadaa gaya tha uske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke sath baithi hui thi ke aik ansariya aurat hamarey yahan aai aur kaha ke Allah falan (Mistah bin asaasa ( ko tabah kar de aur wo usey tabah kar bhi chuka unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine kaha aap ye kya keh rahi hain unhon-ne bataya ke usi ne to ye jhoot mashhoor kya hai. phir ansariya aurat ne ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) par tohmat ka Sara ( waqia bayan kya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne (apni walida se) puchha ke kon sa waqia ? to unki walida ne unhein waaqie ki tafseel bataaii. Aaisha ne puchha ke kya ye qissa Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhi malum ho gaya hai? unki walida ne bataya ke haan. ye suntey hi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) behosh ho kar gir padiin aur jab hosh aaya to jaadey ke sath bukhar chadhaa hua tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur malum farmaya ke unhein kya hua? maine kaha ke aik baat unse aisi kahi gaee thi aur usi ke sadmey se unko bukhar aa gaya hai. phir Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) uth kar baith gain aur kaha Allah ki qasam! agar main qism khaaun jab bhi aap log meri baat nahi maan saktey aur agar koi uzr bayan karun to usey bhi taslim nahi kar saktey. bas meri aur aap logon ki misal Yaqoob (Alaihissalam) aur unke beton ki si hai (ke unhon-ne apne beton ki man-ghadat kahaanii sun kar farmaya tha ke) ''jo kuchh tum keh rahe ho main is par Allah hi ki madad chahta hoon.'' iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif le gaey aur Allah Taala ko jo kuchh manzoor tha wo nazil farmaya, jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iski khabar Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko di to unhon-ne kaha ke uske liye main sirf Allah ka shukr ada karti hun kisi aur ka nahi."
3389,"mujhey Urwa ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aayat ke mutaalliq poochhaa حتى إذا استيأس الرسل وظنوا أنهم قد كذبوا yaanii yahan tak ke jab anbiya naa-ummeed ho gaey aur unhein khayal guzarney laga ke unhein jhutlaa diya gaya to Allah ki madad pahunchi to unhon-ne kaha ke unki qaum ne unhein jhutlaayaa tha. maine arz kya ke phir mana kaisey banengey, paighambaron ko yaqin tha hi ke unki qaum unhein jhutlaa rahi hai. phir Quran mein lafz (ظن‏) guman aur khayal ke mana mein istemal kyon kya gaya? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aey chhotey se Urwa! beshak unko to yaqin tha maine kaha to shayad us aayat main baghair tashdeed ke (كذبوا‏ ( hoga yani paighambar ye samjhey ke Allah ne jo unki madad ka wada kya tha wo ghalat tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : Maaz-Allah ! anbiya apne rab ke sath bhala aisa guman kar saktey hain. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha murad ye hai ke paighambaron ke perokar log jo apne Malik par eman laey they aur paighambaron ki tasdeeq ki thi un par jab muddat tak Allah ki aazmaish rahi aur madad aaney mein der hui aur paighambar log apni qaum ke jhutlaaney walon se naa-ummeed ho gaey (samjhey ke ab wo eman nahi laaengey) aur unhon-ne ye guman kya ke jo log unke perokar baney hain wo bhi unko jhoota samajhney lagengey, us waqt Allah ki madad aan pahunchii. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke sura Yusuf ki aayat ka aik jumla hai yani Zulekha Yusuf (Alaihissalam) se naa-ummeed ho gaii.) yani Allah se ummeed rakho naa-ummeed na ho."
3390,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Shareef-bin-Shareef-bin-Shareef-bin-Shareef Yusuf bin Yaqoob bin Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) hain.''
3391,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Ayyoob (Alaihissalam) nangey ghusl kar rahe they ke soney ki tiddiyaan un par girney lagein . wo unko apne kapdey mein jama karne lagey. unke parwardigar ne unko pukara ke aey Ayyoob! jo kuchh tum dekh rahe ho ( soney ki tiddiyaan ( kya maine tumhen us se be-parwaa nahi kar diya hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke sahi hai, aey rabbul-izzat! lekin teri barkat se main kis tarah be-parwaa ho sakta hoon.''"
3392,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( ghaar hira se) Ummul-Momenin Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ke paas lot aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka dil dhadak raha tha. Khadija (Raziallahu anha) aapko Warqa- bin Nofal ke paas le gain, wo nasrani ho gaey they aur Injeel ko arabii mein padhtey they. Warqa- ne puchha ke aap kya dekhtey hain? aap ne unhein bataya to unhon-ne kaha ke yahi hain wo (naamoos) jinhein Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas bheja tha aur agar main tumharey zamaney tak zinda raha to main tumhari poori madad karunga. (naamoos) mahrame-raaz ya raazdaan insan ko kehtey hain jo aisey raaz se bhi aagah ho jo aadmi dusron se chhipaaey."
3393,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse us raat ke mutaalliq bayan kya jis mein aapko meraaj hua ke jab aap paanchwein aasman par tashrif le gaey to wahan Harun (Alaihissalam) se miley. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne bataya ke ye Harun (Alaihissalam) hain, unhein salam kijiye . maine salam kya to unhon-ne jawab detey huey farmaya : khush aamadeed , Saleh bhai aur Saleh nabii. is hadis ko Qatada ke sath Sabit Bunani aur Ibad bin abi Ali ne bhi Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai."
3394,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us raat ki kaifiyat bayan ki jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko meraaj hua ke maine Musa (Alaihissalam) ko dekha ke wo aik dubley patley seedhey baalon waley aadmi hain. aisa malum hota tha ke qabila shanooh mein se hon aur maine Esa (Alaihissalam) ko bhi dekha, wo miyaanaa qad aur bahut hi zyada surkh w safaid rang waley they. aisey taro-taazaa aur paak w saaf ke malum hota tha ke abhi ghusl khaane se nikley hain aur main Ibrahim se unki aulad mein sabse zyada mushabeh (similar) hun. phir 2 bartan mere samney laey gaey. aik mein doodh tha aur doosrey mein sharab thi. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke donon chizon mein se aap ka jo ji chahey peejiye. maine doodh ka piyala apne hath mein ley liya aur usey pi gaya mujh se kaha gaya ke aap ne fitrat ko ikhtiyar kya (doodh aadmi ki paidaaishii ghizaa hai) agar iske bajaey aap ne sharab pi hoti to aap ki ummat gumrah ho jati."
3395,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi shakhs ko yun na kehna chahiye ke main Yoonus-bin-Mattii se behtar hon, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka naam unke walid ki taraf mansub karke liyaa.''"
3396,Musa (Alaihissalam) gandumi aur daraaz qad they. aisa malum hota tha jaisey qabila shanooh ke koi sahib hon aur farmaya ke Esa (Alaihissalam) ghungariyaaley baal waley aur beech ke qad ke they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne darogha jahannam Malik ka bhi zikr farmaya aur dajjal ka bhii.
3397,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to wahan ke log aik din yani Aashoora ke din roza rakhtey they. un logon ( yahudiyon ( ne bataya ke ye badi azmat wala din hai, isi din Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko nijat di thi aur aal firaun ko gharq kya tha. uske shukr mein Musa (Alaihissalam) ne us din ka roza rakha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Musa (Alaihissalam) ka unse zyada qareeb hun. chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud bhi us din ka roza rakhna shuru kya aur sahaba ko bhi iska hukm farmaayaa."
3398,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din sab log behosh ho jaaeinge, phir sabse pahley mein hosh mein aaoonga aur dekhoonga ke Musa (Alaihissalam) arsh ke paayon mein se aik paaya thaamey huey hain. ab mujhey ye malum nahi ke wo mujh se pahley hosh mein aagey hongey ya (behosh hi nahi kiye gaey hongey balke) unhein koohe-toor ki be-hoshi ka badla mila hoga.''"
3399,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar Bani-Israeel na hotey (salwaa ka gosht jama karke na rakhtey) to gosht kabhi na sadta aur agar Hawwaa na hotiin (yani Adam (Alaihissalam) se daghaa na kartiin) to koi aurat apne shauhar ki khayanat kabhi na karti .''
3400,"Hur-bin-Qais fazari (Raziallahu anhu) se saahibe-Moosaa (Alaihissalam) ke barey mein unka ikhtilaf hua. phir Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) wahan se guzrey to Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bulaya aur kaha ke mera apne un sathi se saahibe-Moosaa (Alaihissalam) ke barey mein ikhtilaf ho gaya hai jin se mulaqat ke liye Musa (Alaihissalam) ne rasta puchha tha, kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap ne unke barey mein kuchh suna hai? unhon-ne farmaya ke ji haan, maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna tha ke Musa (Alaihissalam) Bani-Israeel ki aik jamat mein tashrif rakhtey they ke aik shakhs ne unse poochha, kya aap kisi aisey shakhs ko jantey hain jo is tamam zameen par aap se zyada ilm rakhney wala ho? unhon-ne farmaya ke nahi. is par Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) par wahi nazil ki ke kyon nahi, hamara banda khizr hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne un tak pahunchne ka rasta puchha to unhein machhli ko uski nishani ke taur par bataya gaya aur kaha gaya ke jab machhli gum ho jaey (to jahan gum hui ho wahaan) wapas aa jana wahin unse mulaqat hogi. chunanche Musa (Alaihissalam) dariya mein (safar ke dauraan) machhli ki barabar nigrani kartey rahe. phir unse unke rafeeq safar ne kaha ke aap ne khayal nahi kya jab ham chattaan ke paas thahrey to main machhli ke mutaalliq aapko batana bhool gaya tha aur mujhey shaitan ne usey yad rakhney se ghaafil rakha. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke usi ki to hamein talash hai chunanche ye buzurg usi rastey se peechhey ki taraf lautey aur khizr (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat hui un donon ke hi wo halaat hain jinhein Allah Taala ki kitab mein bayan farmaya hai."
3401,"Nauf Bukaalii ye kehta hai ke Moosaa, saahibe-khizr Bani-Israeel ke Musa nahi hain balke wo doosrey Musa hain. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ke dushman ne bilkul ghalat baat kahi hai. Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey huey ham se bayan kya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) Bani-Israeel ko khadey ho kar Khattab farma rahe they ke unse puchha gaya kon sa shakhs sabse zyada ilm wala hai. unhon-ne farmaya ke main. is par Allah Taala ne un par itaab farmaya kyonke unhon ilm ki nisbat Allah Taala ki taraf nahi ki. Allah Taala ne unse farmaya ke kyon nahi mera aik banda hai jahan 2 dariya aa kar miltey hain wahan rehta hai aur tum se zyada ilm wala hai. unhon-ne arz kya : aey rabbul-aalameen! mein unse kis tarah mil sakoonga? Sufiyan ne (apni riwayat mein ye alfaz ( bayan kiye ke ''aey rab! ( وكيف لي به ( ''Allah taala ne farmaya ke aik machhli pakad kar usey apne thailey mein rakh lenaa, jahan wo machhli gum ho jaey bas mera banda wahin tum ko milega. kuchh baar rawi ne (bajaaey ( فهو ثم ( ke) ( فهو ثمه ( kaha, to Musa (Alaihissalam) ne machhli ley li aur usey aik thailey mein rakh liya. phir wo aur aik unke safar ke sathi Yoosha-bin-Noon rawaana huey, jab ye chattaan par pahunchey to sar se tek laga li, Musa (Alaihissalam) ko neend aa gaee aur machhli tadap kar nikli aur dariya ke andar chali gaee aur usney dariya mein apna rasta bana liya. Allah Taala ne machhli se pani ke bahaao ko rok diya aur wo mehraab ki tarah ho gaee, unhon-ne waazeh kya ke yun mehraab ki tarah. phir ye donon us din aur raat ke baqi hissey mein chaltey rahe, jab doosra din aaya to Musa (Alaihissalam) ne apne safar ke sathi se farmaya ke ab hamara khana lao kyonke ham apne safar mein bahut thak gaey hain. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne us waqt tak koi thakaan mehsus nahi ki thi jab tak wo us muqarrara jagah se aagey na badh gaey jiska Allah Taala ne unhein hukm diya tha. unke rafeeq ne kaha ke dekhiye to sahii jab chattaan par utrey they, to main machhli (ke mutaalliq kahnaa) aap se bhool gaya aur mujhey uski yad se shaitan ne ghaafil rakha aur us machhli ne to wahin (chattaan ke qareeb) dariya mein apna rasta ajeeb taur par bana liya tha. machhli ko to rasta mil gaya aur ye donon hairaan they. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke yahi wo jagah thi jiski talash mein ham nikley hain. chunanche ye donon usi rastey se peechhey ki taraf wapas huey aur jab us chattaan par pahunchey to wahan aik buzurg apna Sara jism aik kapdey mein lapetey huey maujood they. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne unhein salam kya aur unhon-ne jawab diya phir kaha ke tumharey khittey mein salam ka riwaaj kahan se aa gayaa? Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke main Musa hun. unhon-ne poochha, Bani-Israeel ke Moosaa? farmaya ke ji haan. main aap ki khidmat mein isliye hazir hua hun ke aap mujhey wo ilm Naafe sikhaa dein jo aapko sikhaya gaya hai. unhon-ne farmaya : aey Musa ! mere paas Allah ka diya hua aik ilm hai Allah Taala ne mujhey wo ilm sikhaya hai aur aap usko nahi jaantey. isi tarah aap ke paas Allah ka diya hua aik ilm hai Allah Taala ne aapko sikhaya hai aur main usey nahi janta. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : kya main aapke sath reh sakta hoon? unhon-ne kaha ke aap mere sath sabr nahi kar sakengey aur waqei aap un kaamon ke barey mein sabr kar bhi kaisey saktey hain jo aap ke ilm mein nahi hain. Allah Taala ke irshad ( إمرا‏ ( tak. aakhir Musa aur khizr (Alaihissalam) dariya ke kinaarey-kinaarey chaley. phir unke qareeb se aik kashtii guzri. un hazraat ne kaha ke unhein bhi kashtii waley kashtii par Sawar kar lein. kashtii walon ne khizr (Alaihissalam) ko pehchan liya aur koi mazdoorii liye baghair unko sawar kar liya. jab ye hazraat is par Sawar ho gaey to aik chidiyaa aai aur kashtii ke aik kinarey baith kar us ne pani main apni chaunch ko aik ya 2 martaba dala. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : aey Musa ! mere aur aap ke ilm ki wjah se Allah ke ilm mein itni bhi kami nahi hui jitni us chidiyaa ke dariya mein chaunch maarney se dariya ke pani mein kami hui hogi. itney mein khizr (Alaihissalam) ne kulhaadii uthai aur us kashtii mein se aik takhta nikal liya. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne jo nazar uthai to wo apni kulhaadii se takhta nikal chukey they. is par Musa (Alaihissalam) bol padey ke ye aap ne kya kya? jin logon ne hamein baghair kisi ujrat ke sawar kar liya unhein ki kashtii par aap ne buri nazar dali aur usey cheer diya ke sarey kashtii waley doob jaaein. usmein koi shuba nahi ke aap ne bahut hi zyada na-gawar kaam kya. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : kya maine aap se pahley hi nahi keh diya tha ke aap mere sath sabr nahi kar saktey. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke (ye be-sabrii apne wada ko bhool janey ki wjah se hui, isliye) aap us cheez ka mujh se muaakhza na karein jo main bhool gaya tha aur mere mamley mein tangi na farmaaein. ye pehli baat Musa (Alaihissalam) se bhool kar hui thi phir jab dariyaaii safar khatm hua to unka guzar aik bachchey ke paas se hua jo doosrey bachchon ke sath khel raha tha. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne iska sar pakad kar apne hath se ( dhad se) juda kar diya. Sufiyan ne apne hath se ( juda karne ki kaifiyat bataaney ke liye) ishara kya jaisey wo koi cheez tod rahe hun. is par Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke aap ne aik jaan ko zaaye kar diya. kisi dusri jaan ke badley mein bhi ye nahi tha. bila shubah aap ne aik bura kaam kya. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : kya maine aap se pahley hi nahi kaha tha ke aap mere sath sabr nahi kar saktey. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha : achchha iske baad agar maine aap se koi baat poochhi to phir aap mujhey sath na ley chaliyega, beshak aap mere barey mein uzr ki had ko pahunch chukey hain. phir ye donon aagey badhey aur jab aik basti mein pahunchey to basti walon se kaha ke wo unhein apna mehman bana lein, lekin unhon-ne inkar kya. phir us basti mein unhein aik diwar dikhai di jo bas girney hi wali thi. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne apne hath se yun ishara kya. Sufiyan ne ( kaifiyat bataaney ke liye) is tarah ishara kya jaisey wo koi cheez uper ki taraf pher rahe hun. maine Sufiyan se ( مائلا (ka lafz sirf aik martaba suna tha. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke ye log to aisey they ke ham unke yahan aaey aur unhon-ne hamari mezbaanii se bhi inkar kya. phir unki diwar aap ne theek kar di, agar aap chahtey to uski ujrat unse ley saktey they. khizr (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke bas yahan se mere aur aap ke darmyan judai ho gaee jin baton par aap sabr nahi kar saktey, mein unki taaweel aur taujeeh ab tum par waazeh kar doonga. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hamari to khahish ye thi ke Musa (Alaihissalam) sabr kartey aur Allah Taala takweenii (Allah ki taraf se fix) waaqiaat hamarey liye bayan karta. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala Musa (Alaihissalam) par raham karey, agar unhon-ne sabr kya hota to unke (mazeed waaqiaat) hamein malum hotey. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aam qirat ( ودرائهم (ke bajaey) ( أمامهم ملك يأخذ كل سفينة صالحة غصبا ( padha hai. aur wo bachcha ( jiski khizr (Alaihissalam) ne jaan li thi) kaafir tha aur uske waalidain momin they. phir mujh se Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke maine ye hadis Amr-bin-Dinar se 2 martaba suni thi aur unhiin se (sun kar) yad ki thi. Sufiyan ne kisi se puchha tha ke kya ye hadis aap ne Amr-bin-Dinar se sunney se pahley hi kisi doosrey shakhs se sun kar (jisne Amr-bin-Dinar se suni ho) yad ki thi? ya (iske bajaey ye jumla kaha) ( تحفظته من إنسان ( 2 martaba (shak Ali-bin-Abdullaah ko tha) to Sufiyan ne kaha ke doosrey kisi shakhs se sun kar main yad karta, kya is hadis ko Amr-bin-Dinar se mere siwa kisi aur ne bhi riwayat kya hai? maine unse ye hadis 2 ya teen martaba suni aur unhiin se sun kar yad ki."
3402,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''khizr (Alaihissalam) ka ye naam is wjah se hua ke wo aik sookhii zameen (jahaan sabzii ka naam bhi na tha) par baithey. lekin joon hi wo wahan se uthey to wo jagah sar-sabz ho kar lahlahaaney lagii.''
3403,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''banii-Israaeel ko hukm hua tha ke baitul-maqdis mein sajda w rukoo kartey huey dakhil hon aur ye kehtey huey ke ya Allaah! ham ko bakhsh de. lekin unhon-ne usko ulta kya aur apne koolhon ke bal ghisat'tey huey dakhil huey aur ye kehtey huey (حبة في شعرة) (yaanii baaliyon mein daney khub hon) dakhil huey.''
3404,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Musa (Alaihissalam) badey hi sharm waley aur badan dhaanpney waley they. unki haya ki wjah se unke badan ko koi hissey bhi nahi dekha ja sakta tha. Bani-Israeel ke jo log unhein azeeyat pahunchaney ke dar pai they, wo kyon baaz reh saktey they, un logon ne kehna shuru kya ke is darje badan chhipaaney ka ehtimaam sirf isliye hai ke unke jism mein aib hai ya kodh hai ya unke ghadood badhey huey hain ya phir koi aur bimari hai. idhar Allah Taala ko ye manzoor hua ke Musa (Alaihissalam) ki unki ghalatiyon se paakii dikhlaaye. aik din Musa (Alaihissalam) akeley ghusl karne ke liye aaey aik patthar par apne kapdey (utaar kar) rakh diye. phir ghusl shuru kya. jab farigh huey to kapdey uthaney ke liye badhey lekin patthar unke kapdon samet bhaagney laga. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne apna asaa uthaya aur patthar ke peechhey daudey. ye kehtey huey ke patthar! mera kapda de-dey. aakhir Bani-Israeel ki aik jamat tak pahunch gaey aur un sab ne aapko nangaa dekh liya, Allah ki makhlooq mein sabse behtar haalat mein aur is tarah Allah Taala ne unki tohmat se unki Bara't (najaat) kar di. ab patthar bhi ruk gaya aur aap ne kapda utha kar pahnaa. phir patthar ko apne asaa se maarney lagey. Allah ki qism us patthar par Musa (Alaihissalam) ke maarney ki wjah se teen ya char ya panch jagah nishan pad gaey they. Allah Taala ke is farmaan يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تكونوا كالذين آذوا موسى فبرأه الله مما قالوا وكان عند الله وجيها ''tum unki tarah na ho jana jinhoney Musa (Alaihissalam) ko takleef di thi, phir unki tohmat se Allah Taala ne unhein barii qarar diya aur wo Allah ki bargah mein badi shaan waley aur izzat waley they. ''main usi waaqie ki taraf ishara hai."
3405,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik martaba maal taqseem kya, aik shakhs ne kaha ke ye aik aisi taqseem hai jis mein Allah ki raza jooii ka koi lihaaz nahi kya gaya. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar aapko uski khabar di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghussa huey aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehre par ghussey ke aasaar dekhey. phir farmaya, Allah Taala Musa (Alaihissalam) par raham farmaaey, unko is se bhi zyada takleef di gaee thi magar unhon-ne sabr kya."
3406,"(eik martaba) ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (safar mein) peelu ke phal todney lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo siyah hon unhein todo, kyonke wo zyada lazeez hota hai. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : kya aap ne kabhi bakriyan charaaii hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi Nabi aisa nahi guzra jisne bakriyan na charaaii hun."
3407,"Allah Taala ne Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas malakul-maut ko bhejaa. jab malakul-maut Musa (Alaihissalam) ke paas aaey to unhon-ne unhein chaantaa maara (kyonke wo insan ki sura mein aaya tha) malakul-maut , Allah rabbul-izzat ki bargah mein wapas huey aur arz kya ke tu ney apne aik aisey bandey ke paas mujhey bheja jo maut ke liye taiyaar nahi hai. Allah Taala ne farmaya ke dobara unke paas jao aur kaho ke apna hath kisi bail ki peeth par rakhein, unke hath mein jitney baal iske aa jayen unmein se har baal ke badley aik saal ki umr unhein di jaeygi (malakul-maut dobara aaey aur Allah Taala ka faisla sunaayaa) Musa (Alaihissalam) boley : aey rab! phir iske baad kya hoga? Allah Taala ne farmaya ke phir maut hai. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne arz kya ke phir abhi kyon na aa jaey. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Musa (Alaihissalam) ne Allah Taala se dua ki ke baitul-maqdis se mujhey itna qareeb kar diya jaey ke (jahaan unki qabr ho wahan se) agar koi patthar phainkey to wo baitul-maqdis tak pahunch sakey. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar main wahan maujood hota to baitul-maqdis mein, main tumhen unki qabr dikhaataa jo rastey ke kinarey par hai, ret ke surkh teeley se neechey. abdur-Razzaaq-bin-Hammaam ne bayan kya ke hamein Mamar ne khabar di, unhein Hammam ne aur unko Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah bayan kya."
3408,"musalmanon ki jamat ke aik aadmi aur yahudiyon mein se aik shakhs ka jhagdaa hua. musalman ne kaha ke us zaat ki qism jisne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko saari duniya mein barguzeeda banaya, qism khaatey huey unhon-ne ye kaha, is par Yahudi ne kaha : qism hai us zaat ki jisne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko saari duniya mein barguzeeda banaya. is par musalman ne apna hath utha kar Yahudi ko thappad mar diya. wo yahoodii, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur apne aur musalman ke jhagdey ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi mauqe par farmaya ke mujhey Musa (Alaihissalam) par tarjeeh na diya karo. log qiyamat ke din behosh kar diye jaeinge aur sabse pahley main hosh mein aaoonga phir dekhoonga ke Musa (Alaihissalam) arsh ka paaya pakdey huey khadey hain. ab mujhey malum nahi ke wo bhi behosh honey walon mein they aur mujh se pahley hi hosh mein aagey ya unhein Allah Taala ne behosh honey walon mein hi nahi rakha tha."
3409,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Moosaa aur Adam (Alaihissalam) ne aapas mein bahas ki. Musa (Alaihissalam) ne unse kaha ke aap Adam hain jinhein unki khata ne jannat se nikaalaa. Adam (Alaihissalam) boley aur aap Musa (Alaihissalam) hain ke jinhein Allah Taala ne apni risalat aur apne kalam se nawaazaa, phir bhi aap mujhey aik aisey mamley par malaamat kartey hain jo Allah Taala ne meri paidaaish se bhi pahley muqaddar kar diyaa.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''to Adam (al), Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aa gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye jumla 2 martaba farmaayaa."
3410,aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya '' mere samney tamam ummatein laai gain aur maine dekha ke aik bahut badi jamat aasman ke kinaron par chhaaii hui hai. phir bataya gaya ke ye apni qaum ke sath Musa (Alaihissalam) hain.''
3411,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mardon main to bahut se kaamil log uthey lekin aurton mein firaun ki biwi aasiya aur maryam-binte-Imraan (Alaihissalam) ke siwa aur koi kaamil nahi paida hui, haan aurton par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki fazeelat aisi hai jaisey tamam khaanon par sareed ki fazeelat hai.''"
3412,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii shakhs mere mutaalliq ye na kahey ke main Yunus (Alaihissalam) se behtar hoon.'' Musaddad ne Yoonus-bin-Matti (Alaihissalam) ke lafz badha kar riwayat kya.
3413,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi shakhs ke liye munasib nahi ke mujhey Yoonus-bin-Mattii se behtar qarar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke walid ki taraf mansub karke unka naam liya tha.''
3414,"aik martaba logon ko aik Yahudi apna saman dikhaa raha tha lekin usey uski jo qeemat lagai gaee is par wo razi na tha. isliye kehney laga ke hargiz nahi, us zaat ki qism jisne Musa ko tamam insanon mein barguzeeda qarar diya. ye lafz aik Ansari sahabi ne sun liye aur khadey ho kar unhon-ne aik thappad uske munh par maara aur kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi ham mein maujood hain aur to is tarah qism khata hai ke us zaat ki qism jisne Musa (Alaihissalam) ko tamam insanon mein barguzeeda qarar diya. is par wo Yahudi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey abul-Qaasim! mera musalmanon ke sath amn aur suleh ka ahad w paiman hai. phir falan shakhs ka kya haal hoga jisne mere munh par chaantaa maara hai, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us sahabi se malum farmaya ke tum ne iske munh par kyon chaantaa maara ? unhon-ne wjah bayan ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghussey ho gaey is qadr ke ghussey ke aasaar chehre par numaayaan ho gaey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ke anbiya mein aapas mein aik ko doosrey par fazeelat na diya karo, jab Saur phoonkaa jaeyga to aasman w zameen ki tamam makhlooq par be-hoshi taarii ho jaeygi, siwa unke jinhein Allah Taala chaahega. phir dusri martaba Saur phoonkaa jaeyga aur sabse pahley mujhey uthaya jaeyga, lekin main dekhoonga ke Musa (Alaihissalam) arsh ko pakdey huey khadey hongey, ab mujhey malum nahi ke ye unhein taur ki be-hoshi ka badla diya gaya hoga ya mujh se bhi pahley unki be-hoshi khatm kar di gaee hogi."
3415,aur main to ye bhi nahi keh sakta ke koi shakhs Yoonus-bin-Matti se behtar hai.
3416,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi shakhs ke liye ye kehna laaiq nahi ke main Yoonus-bin-Matti se afzal hoon.''
3417,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''daawood (Alaihissalam) ke liye Quran (yani Zaboor) ki qirat bahut aasan kar di gaee thi. chunanche wo apni sawari par zeen kasney ka hukm detey aur zeen kasi janey se pahley hi poori Zabur padh letey they aur aap sirf apne hathon ki kamaaii khaatey they.'' iski riwayat Musa-bin-Aqba ne ki, unse Safwan ne, unse Ata-bin-Yasar ne, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai."
3418,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar mili ke maine kaha hai ke Allah ki qasam, jab tak main zinda rahoonga, din mein rozey rakhoonga aur raat bhar ibadat kya karunga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha ke kya tumhii ne ye kaha hai ke Allah ki qism jab tak zinda rahunga din bhar rozey rakhoonga aur raat bhar ibadat karoonga? maine arz kya ji haan maine ye jumla kaha hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum usey nibhaa nahi sakogey, isliye roza bhi rakha karo aur baghair rozey ke bhi raha karo aur raat mein ibadat bhi kya karo aur soyaa bhi karo. har mahiney mein teen din roza rakha karo, kyonke har neki ka badla das guna milta hai is tarah roze ka ye tariqa bhi) sawab ke eitibaar se) zindagi bhar ke rozey jaisa ho jaeyga maine kaha ke main us se afzal tareeqe ki taqat rakhta hun. aey Allah ke rasool! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke phir aik din roza rakha karo aur 2 din baghair rozey ke raha karo. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya ke main is se bhi afzal tareeqey ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir aik din roza rakha karo aur aik din baghair roze ke raha karo. Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey ka tariqa bhi yahi tha aur yahi sabse afzal tariqa hai. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main us se bhi afzal tareeqey ki taqat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is se afzal aur koi tariqa nahi."
3419,"mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ''kya meri ye khabar sahi hai ke tum raat bhar ibadat kartey ho aur din bhar (rozaana) roza rakhtey ho?'' maine arz kya ke ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lekin tum isi tarah kartey rahe to tumhari aankhen kamzor ho jaeyngi aur tumhara ji uktaa jaeyga har mahiney mein teen rozey rakha karo ke yahi (sawab ke eitibaar se) zindagi bhar ka roza hai, ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) zindagi bhar ke rozey ki tarah hai. maine arz kya ke main apne mein mehsus karta hun, Misar ne bayan kya ke aap ki murad quwwat se thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke rozey ki tarah rozey rakha karo. wo aik din rozey rakha kartey aur aik din baghair rozey ke raha kartey they aur dushman se muqaabla kartey to maidan se bhaagaa nahi kartey they."
3420,"mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ''Allah taala ke nazdeek rozey ka sabse pasandida tariqa Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka tariqa tha. aap aik din roza rakhtey aur aik din baghair rozey ke rahtey they. isi tarah Allah Taala ke nazdeek Namaz ka sabse zyada pasandida tariqa Dawud (Alaihissalam) ki Namaz ka tariqa tha, aap aadhi raat tak sotey aur aik tehai hissey mein ibadat kya kartey they, phir Baqiiya chhatey hissey mein bhi sotey they.''"
3421,"maine Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya main sura Swaad mein sajda kya karun? to unhon-ne aayat ومن ذريته Dawud وسليمان tilaawat ki) فبهداهم اقتده‏ ( tak neez unhon-ne kaha ke tumharey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un logon mein se they jinhein anbiya (Alaihissalam) ki iqtida (pairvi) ka hukm tha."
3422,"sura Swaad ka sajda zaroori nahi, lekin maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is sura mein sajda kartey dekha hai."
3423,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''eik sarkash jin kal raat mere samney aa gaya, taake meri Namaz kharaab kar de lekin Allah Taala ne mujhey is par qudrat de di aur maine usey pakad liya. phir maine chaha ke usey masjid ke kisi sutoon se baandh dun ke tum sab log bhi dekh sako. lekin mujhey apne bhai Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ki dua yad aa gaee ke ya Allaah! mujhey aisi saltanat de jo mere siwa kisi ko muyassar na ho. isliye maine usey naa-muraad wapas kar diya. (ifreet) sarkash ke mana mein hai, chahe insanon mein se ho ya jinon mein se.''"
3424,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Sulaimaan-bin-Daawood (Alaihissalam) ne kaha ke aaj raat main apni 70 beeviyon ke paas jaaunga aur har biwi aik shehsawaar janegi jo Allah ke rastey mein jihad karega. unke sathi ne kaha insha'allah, lekin unhon-ne nahi kaha. chunanche kisi biwi ke yahan bhi bachcha paida nahi hua, sirf aik ke yahan hua aur uski bhi aik taraf bekaar thii.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) inshaAllah keh letey (to sab ke yahan bachchey paida hotey) aur Allah ke rastey mein jihad kartey. (Shuaib aur ibne- abii-Zinaad ne bajaey 70 ke) nawwey kaha hai aur yahi bayan zyada sahi hai."
3425,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : ya Rasulullah ! sabse pahley kon si masjid banai gaee thi? farmaya ke masjide-Haraam ! maine sawal kya, iske baad kon sii? farmaya ke masjide-Aqsaa. maine sawal kya aur un donon ki tameer ka darmyani fasla kitna tha? farmaya ke chalis (40) saal . phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis jagah bhi Namaz ka waqt ho jaey fauran Namaz padh lo. tumharey liye poori zameen masjid hai."
3426,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri aur tamam insanon ki misal aik aisey shakhs ki si hai jisne aag roshan ki ho. phir parwaaney aur keedey-makodey usmein girney lagey hoon.''
3427,"2 auratein thin aur donon ke sath donon ke bachchey they. itney mein aik bhediyaa aaya aur aik aurat ke bachchey ko utha ley gaya. un donon mein se aik aurat ne kaha bhediyaa tumharey betey ko ley gaya hai aur dusri ne kaha ke tumharey betey ko ley gaya hai. donon Dawud (Alaihissalam) ke yahan apna muqaddima le gain . aap ne badi aurat ke haq mein faisla kar diya. uske baad wo donon Sulaimaan-bin-Daawood (Alaihissalam) ke yahan aaiin aur unhein us jhagdey ki khabar di. unhon-ne farmaya ke achchha chhuri laao. is bachchey ke 2 tukdey karke donon ke darmyan baant dun. chhoti aurat ne ye sun kar kaha : Allah aap par raham farmaai aisa na keejiye, maine maan liya ke usi badi ka ladka hai. is par Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ne us chhoti ke haq mein faisla kya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine (sikkeen) ka lafz isi din suna, warna ham hamesha (chhurii ke liye) (مدية‏) ka lafz bola kartey they."
3428,jab aayat ( الذين آمنوا ولم يلبسوا إيمانهم بظلم‏ ( ''jo log eman laey aur apne eman mein zulm ki milawat nahi ki.'' nazil hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ne arz kya ham mein aisa kon hoga jisne apne eman mein zulm nahi kya hoga. is par ye aayat nazil huii لا تشرك بالله إن الشرك لظلم عظيم''Allaah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraa. beshak shirk hi zulme-azeem hai.''
3429,"jab aayat ( الذين آمنوا ولم يلبسوا إيمانهم بظلم‏ ( ''jo log eman laey aur apne eman ke sath zulm ki milawat nahi ki.'' naazil hui to musalmanon par bada sakht guzra aur unhon-ne arz kya ham mein kon aisa ho sakta hai jisne apne eman ke sath zulm ki milawat na ki hogii? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iska ye matlab nahi, zulm se murad aayat mein shirk hai. kya tum ne nahi suna ke luqman (Alaihissalam) ne apne betey se kaha tha usey nasihat kartey huey ke aey betey ! Allah Taala ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thehra , beshak shirk bada hi zulm hai."
3430,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shab meraaj ke mutaalliq bayan farmaya ke phir aap uper chadhey aur doosrey aasman par tashrif ley gaey. phir darwaza kholney ke liye kaha, puchha gaya : kon hain? kaha ke Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) . puchha gaya : aap ke sath kon hain? kaha ke Muhammad (sl). puchha gaya : kya unhein laney ke liye bhejaa, kaha ke ji haan. phir jab main wahan pahuncha to Esa aur Yahya (Alaihissalam) wahan maujood they. ye donon Nabi aapas mein khaala-zaad bhai hain. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne bataya ke ye Yahya aur Esa (Alaihissalam) hain. unhein salam keejiye. maine salam kya, donon ne jawab diya aur kaha khush aamadeed nek bhai aur nek nabii."
3431,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''har aik insan jab paida hota hai to paidaaish ke waqt shaitan usey chhootaa hai aur bachcha shaitan ke chhooney se zor se cheekhta hai. siwaey Maryam aur unke betey Esa (Alaihissalam) ke.'' phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) uski wjah Maryam (Alaihissalam) ki walida ki dua hai ke aey Allah ! ( main usey (Maryam ko) aur uski aulad ko shaitaane-rajeem se teri panah mein deti hun."
3432,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke Maryam-binte-Imraan (apne zamana mein) sabse behtreen khatun thin aur is ummat ki sabse behtreen khatun Khadija hain (Raziallahu anhu) ."
3433,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aurton par Aaisha ki fazeelat aisey hai jaisey tamam khaanon par sareed ki. mardon mein se to bahut se kaamil ho guzrey hain lekin aurton mein Maryam-binte-Imraan aur Firaun ki biwi Aasiya ke siwa aur koi kaamil paida nahi huii.''
3434,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke oont par Sawar honey waaliyon ( arabii khawaateen ( mein sabse behtreen qureshi khawaateen hain. apne bachchey par sabse zyada mohabbat w shafqat karne wali aur apne shauhar ke maal w asbaab ki sabse behtar nigraan w muhaafiz. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ye hadis bayan karne ke baad kehtey they ke Maryam binte- Imran oont par kabhi sawar nahi hui thin. Yunus ke sath is hadis ko Zohri ke bhatijey aur Ishaq kalbi ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya hai."
3435,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jisne gawahi di ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi, wo yakta aur la Sharik hai aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske bandey aur rasool hain aur ye ke Esa (Alaihissalam) uske bandey aur rasool hain aur uska kalima hain, jisey pahuncha diya tha Allah ne Maryam tak aur aik Rooh hain uski taraf se aur ye ke jannat haq hai aur dozakh haq hai to usne jo bhi amal kya hoga (aakhir) Allah Taala usey jannat mein dakhil karega. ''Waleed ne bayan kya, ke mujh se ibne- Jaabir ne bayan kya, unse Umer ne aur junaada ne aur apni riwayat mein ye zyada kya (aisaa shakhs) jannat ke aath (8) darwazon mein se jis se chahey (daakhil hoga)."
3436,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''god mein teen bachchon ke siwa aur kisi ne baat nahi ki. awwal Esa (Alaihissalam) (doosrey ka waqia ye hai ke) Bani-Israeel mein aik buzurg they, naam Juraij tha. wo Namaz padh rahe they ke unki maan ne unhein pukaaraa. unhon-ne (apne dil mein) kaha ke main walida ka jawab dun ya Namaz padhta rahun? is par unki walida ne (ghussa ho kar) baddua ki : aey Allaah! us waqt tak usey maut na aaey jab tak ye zaaniya aurton ka munh na dekh ley. Juraij apne ibadat khaney mein raha kartey they. aik martaba unke samney aik faahisha aurat aai aur unse badkaarii chahi lekin unhon-ne ( uski khahish poori karne se) inkar kya. phir aik charwaahey ke paas aai aur usey apne uper qaabu de diya us se aik bachcha paida hua aur us ne un par ye tohmat dharii ke ye Juraij ka bachcha hai. unki qaum ke log aaey aur unka ibadat khaana tod diya, unhein nichey utaar kar laey aur unhein gaaliyaan din. phir unhon-ne wuzu karke Namaz padhi, iske baad bachchey ke paas aaey aur us se puchha ke tera bap kon hai? bachcha (Allah ke hukm se) bol padaa ke charwaha hai is par (unki qaum sharminda hui aur) kaha ham aap ka ibadat khaana soney ka banaaengey. lekin unhon-ne kaha hargiz nahi, mitti hi ka banega (teesraa waaqia) aur aik Bani-Israeel ki aurat thi, apne bachchey ko doodh pilaa rahi thi. qareeb se aik sawar bahut hi zyada izzat wala aur achchhey libaas wala guzraa. us aurat ne dua ki : aey Allaah! mere bachchey ko bhi usi jaisa bana de lekin bachcha (Allah ke hukm se) bol padaa ke aey Allaah! mujhey us jaisa na banaanaa. phir uske seeney se lag kar doodh peeney laga. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jaisey main is waqt bhi dekh raha hun ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni ungli choos rahe hain (bachchey ke doodh peeney ki kaifiyat batlatey waqt) phir aik baandi uske qareeb se ley jaaii gaee (jisey uske Malik mar rahe they) to us aurat ne dua ki ke aey Allaah! mere bachchey ko us jaisa na banaanaa. bachchey ne phir uska pistaan chhod diya aur kaha ke aey Allah ! mujhey usi jaisa bana de. us aurat ne poochha. aisa to kyon keh raha hai? bachchey ne kaha ke wo sawar zaalimon mein se aik zaalim shakhs tha aur us baandi se log keh rahe they ke tum ne chori ki aur zina kya halanke us ne kuchh bhi nahi kya tha."
3437,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis raat meri meraaj hui, maine Musa (Alaihissalam) se mulaqat ki thi. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka huliya bayan kya wo . . . . mera khayal hai ke Mamar ne kaha, . . . daraaz qaamat aur seedhey baalon waley they jaisey qabila shanooh ke log hotey hain. aap ne bayan kya ke maine Esa (Alaihissalam) se bhi mulaqat ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka bhi huliya bayan farmaya ke darmyaana qad aur surkh w safed they, jaisey abhi abhii ghusl khaney se bahar aaey hon aur maine Ibrahim se bhi mulaqat ki thi aur main unki aulad mein unse sabse zyada mushabeh (similar) hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere paas 2 bartan laey gaey, aik mein doodh tha aur doosrey mein sharab mujh se kaha gaya ke jo aap ka ji chahey ley lo. maine doodh ka bartan ley liya aur pi liya. is par mujh se kaha gaya ke fitrat ki aap ne raah pa li, ya fitrat ko aap ne pa liya. iske bajaey agar aap sharab ka bartan letey to aap ki ummat gumrah ho jati."
3438,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' maine Esa , Musa aur Ibrahim ko dekha. Esa (Alaihissalam) bahut hi zyada surkh ghunghraaley baal waley aur chaudey seeney waley they aur Musa (Alaihissalam) gehunwey rang ke daraaz qaamat aur seedhey baalon waley they jaisey koi qabila zat ka aadmi ho.''"
3439,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik din logon ke samney dajjal ka zikr kya aur farmaya ke ismein koi shuba nahi ke Allah Taala kaana nahi hai, lekin dajjal dahini aankh se kaana hoga, uski aankh uthey huey angoor ki tarah hogi."
3440,"aur maine raat Kaba ke paas khuwab mein aik gehunwey rang ke aadmi ko dekha jo gehunwey rang ke aadmiyon mein shakl ke eitibaar se sabse zyada khoobsurat tha. iske sar ke baal shaanon tak latak rahe they, sar se pani tapak raha tha aur donon hath 2 aadmiyon ke kandhon par rakhey huey wo Baitullah ka tawaaf kar rahe they. maine puchha ye kon buzurg hain? to farishton ne bataya ke ye Masih ibne-Maryam hain. iske baad maine aik shakhs ko dekha, sakht aur mudey huey baalon wala jo dahini aankh se kaana tha. usey maine ibne-qatan se sabse zyada shakl mein milta hua paya, wo bhi aik shakhs ke shaanon par apne donon hath rakhey huey Baitullah ka tawaaf kar raha tha. maine poochha, ye kon hain? farishton ne bataya ke ye dajjal hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ubaidullah ne Naafe se ki hai."
3441,"hargiz nahi. Allah ki qism Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Esa (Alaihissalam) ke barey mein ye nahi farmaya tha ke wo surkh they balke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya tha ke maine khuwab mein aik martaba Baitullah ka tawaaf kartey huey apne ko dekha, us waqt mujhey aik sahib nazar aaey jo gehunwey rang latkey huey baal waley they, 2 aadmiyon ke darmyan unka sahara liye huey aur sar se pani saaf kar rahe they. maine puchha ke aap kon hain? to farishton ne jawab diya ke aap ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) hain. is par maine unhein ghaur se dekha to mujhey aik aur shakhs bhi dikhai diya jo surkh, motaa, sar ke baal mudey huey aur dahini aankh se kaana tha, uski aankh aisi dikhai deti thi jaisey utha hua anaar ho, maine puchha ye kon hai? to farishton ne bataya ke ye dajjal hai. is se shakl w sura mein ibne- qatan bahut zyada mushabeh (similar) tha. Zohri ne kaha ke ye qabila khuza'aa ka aik shakhs tha jo jahiliyat ke zamane mein mar gaya tha."
3442,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahey they ke main ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) se dusron ke muqaabley mein zyada qareeb hun, anbiya allaatii bhaiyon ki tarah hain aur mere aur Esa (Alaihissalam) ke darmyan koi Nabi nahi hai."
3443,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main Eisaa-bin-Maryam (Alaihissalam) se aur logon ke muqaabley zyada qareeb hun, duniya mein bhi aur aakhirat mein bhi aur anbiya (Alaihissalam) allaatii bhaiyon (ki tarah) hain. unke masayel mein agarche ikhtilaf hai lekin Deen sab ka aik hi hai.'' aur Ibrahim bin Tahmaan ne bayan kya, unse Musa-bin-Aqba ne, unse Safwaan-bin-Sulaim ne, unse Ata-bin-Yasar ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa."
3444,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Eisaa ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ne aik shakhs ko chori kartey huey dekha phir us se malum farmaya : tu ney chori ki hai? usne kaha hargiz nahi, us zaat ki qism jiske siwa aur koi maabood nahi. Esa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya ke main Allah par eman laya aur meri aankhon ko dhokaa hua.''"
3445,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mujhey mere martabey se zyada na badhaao jaisey Esa ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ko nasara ne unke rutbey se zyada badha diya hai. main to sirf Allah ka banda hun, isliye yahi kaha karo (mere mutaalliq) ke main Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hoon.''"
3446,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan farmaya ''agar koi shakhs apni londi ko achi tarah adab sikhlaaey aur poorey taur par usey Deen ki taleem de. phir usey aazad karke us se nikah kar ley to usey 2 guna sawab milta hai aur wo shakhs jo pahley Esa (Alaihissalam) par eman rakhta tha, phir mujh par eman laya to usey bhi 2 guna sawab milta hai aur wo ghulam jo apne rab ka bhi dar rakhta hai aur apne aaqa ki bhi itaat karta hai to usey bhi 2 guna sawab milta hai.''"
3447,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(qiyaamat ke din) tum log nangey paaun, nangey badan aur baghair khatna ke uthaey jao gey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is aayat ki tilawat ki ''jis tarah ham ne unhein pehli martaba paida kya tha isi tarah ham dobara lautaaengey, ye hamari taraf se wada hai aur beshak ham usey karne waley hain.'' phir sabse pahley Ibrahim ko kapda pahnaayaa jaeyga phir mere ashaab ko daain (jannat ki) taraf ley jaya jaeyga lekin kuchh ko baain (jahannam ki) taraf ley jaya jaeyga main kahunga ke ye to mere ashaab hain lekin mujhey bataya jaeyga ke jab aap unse juda huey to usi waqt unhon-ne irtidaad (Islam se phir jana) ikhtiyar kar liya tha. main us waqt wahi kahunga jo Allah ke nek bandey Esa ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ne kaha tha ke jab tak mein unmein maujood tha unki nigrani karta raha lekin jab tu ney mujhey utha liya to to hi unka nigahbaan hai aur to har cheez par nigahbaan hai. aayat ( ‏‏‏‏العزيز الحكيم‏ ( tak Muhammad-bin-Yoosuf ne bayan kya ke abu-Adbullah se riwayat hai aur unse Qabisa ne bayan kya ke ye wo murtadeen hain jinhoney Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke daure-khilaafat mein kufr ikhtiyar kya tha aur jin se Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jang ki thi."
3448,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, wo zamana qareeb hai ke Esa ibne-Maryam (Alaihissalam) tumharey darmyan aik aadil Hakim ki haisiyat se nazil hongey. wo saleeb ko tod dengey , Sura ko mar daalengey aur jiziya mauqoof (hataa) kar dengey. us waqt maal ki itni kasarat ho jaeygi ke koi usey leney wala nahi milega. us waqt ka aik sajda (duniya aur jo kuchh usmein hai) se badh kar hoga. phir Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke agar tumhara ji chahey to ye aayat padh lo وإن من أهل الكتاب إلا ليؤمنن به قبل موته ويوم القيامة يكون عليهم شهيدا '' aur koi ahle-kitab aisa nahi hoga jo Esa ki maut se pahley is par eman na laey aur qiyamat ke din wo un par gawah hongey.''"
3449,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tumhaaraa us waqt kya haal hoga jab Esa ibne-Maryam tum mein utrengey (tum Namaz padh rahe hogey (aur tumhara imam tum hi mein se hoga.'' is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Aqeel aur Auzai ne ki.
3450,"Aqba-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, kya aap wo hadis ham se nahi bayan karengey jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi? unhon-ne kaha ke maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna tha ke jab dajjal niklega to uske sath aag aur pani donon hongey lekin logon ko jo aag dikhai degi wo thanda pani hoga aur logon ko jo thanda pani dikhai dega to wo jalaaney wali aag hogi. isliye tum mein se jo koi uske zamaney mein ho to usey usmein girnaa chahiye jo aag hogi kyonke wahi intihai sheereen aur thanda pani hoga."
3451,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna tha ke pahley zamaney mein aik shakhs ke paas malakul-maut unki Rooh qabz karne aaey to unse puchha gaya koi apni neki tumhen yad hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey to yad nahi padtii . unse dobara kaha gaya ke yad karo ! unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey koi apni neki yad nahi, siwa iske ke main duniya mein logon ke sath khareed w farokht kya karta tha aur lein-dein kya karta tha, jo log khush'haal hotey unhein to main (apnaa qarz wsool kartey waqt) mohlat diya karta tha aur tang hath walon ko maaf kar diya karta tha. Allah Taala ne unhein usi par jannat mein dakhil kya."
3452,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna ke aik shakhs ki maut ka jab waqt aa gaya aur wo apni zindagi se bilkul maayoos ho gaya to usne apne ghar walon ko wasiiyat ki ke jab meri maut ho jaey to mere liye bahut saari lakdiyan jama karna aur unmein aag laga dena. jab aag mere gosht ko jalaa chukey aur aakhiri haddi ko bhi jalaa de to un jalii hui haddiyon ko pees daalnaa aur kisi tund hua waley din ka intizar karna aur) aisey kisi din) meri raakh ko dariya mein baha dena. iske ghar walon ne aisa hi kya. lekin Allah Taala ne uski raakh ko jama kya aur us se puchha aisa tu ney kyon karwaya tha? us ne jawab diya ke terey hi khof se aey Allah ! Allah Taala ne usi wjah se uski maghfirat farma di. Aqba-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine aapko ye farmatey suna tha ke ye shakhs kafan chor tha.
3453,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jaan nikalney ki haalat taarii hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni chadar chehra Mubarak par baar-baar daal letey phir jab shiddat badhtii to usey hata detey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi haalat mein farmaya tha, Allah ki laanat ho yahood w nasara par ke unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko sajda gaah bana liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is ummat ko unke kiye se daraanaa chahtey they."
3454,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jaan nikalney ki haalat taarii hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni chadar chehra Mubarak par baar-baar daal letey phir jab shiddat badhtii to usey hata detey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi haalat mein farmaya tha, Allah ki laanat ho yahood w nasara par ke unhon-ne apne anbiya ki qabron ko sajda gaah bana liya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is ummat ko unke kiye se daraanaa chahtey they."
3455,"mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki majlis mein panch saal tak betha hun. maine unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ye hadis bayan kartey suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''banii-Israaeel ke anbiya unki siyaasi rehnumai bhi kya kartey they, jab bhi unka koi Nabi halaak ho jata to doosrey unki jagah aa maujood hotey, lekin yad rakho mere baad koi Nabi nahi aayega. haan mere naaib hongey aur bahut hongey. sahaba ne arz kya ke unke mutaalliq aap ka hamein kya hukm hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sabse pahley jis se bait kar lo, bas usi ki wafaadaarii par qaaim raho aur unka jo haq hai uski adaaeygi mein kotahi na karo kyonke Allah Taala unse qiyamat ke din unki riaya ke barey mein sawal karega.''"
3456,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum log pehli ummaton ke tariqon ki qadam-b-qadam pairwi karogey yahan tak ke agar wo log kisi saahina ke suraakh mein dakhil huey to tum bhi usmein dakhil hogey. ham ne puchha ya Rasulullah (sl)! kya aap ki murad pehli ummaton se yahood w nasara hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir kon ho sakta hai?''
3457,"(namaz ke liye elaan ke tareeqey par bahas kartey waqt) sahaba ne aag aur naaqoos ka zikr kya, lekin kuchh ne kaha ke ye to yahood w nasara ka tariqa hai. aakhir Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm hua ke azan main ( kalimaat ( 2-2 baar kahein aur takbeer mein eik-eik baar."
3458,Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kokh par hath rakhney ko na-pasand karti thin aur farmati thin ke is tarah yahood kartey hain.
3459,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tumhaaraa zamana pichhli ummaton ke muqaabley mein aisa hai jaisey Asr se maghrib tak ka waqt hai, tumhari misal yahood w nasara ke sath aisi hai jaisey kisi shakhs ne kuchh mazdoor liye aur kaha ke mera kaam aadhey din tak kon eik-eik qirat ki ujrat par karega? yahood ne aadhey din tak eik-eik qirat ki mazdoorii par kaam karna tay kar liya. phir us shakhs ne kaha ke aadhey din se Asr ki Namaz tak mera kaam kon shakhs eik-eik qirat ki mazdoorii par karega . ab nasara eik-eik qirat ki mazdoorii par aadhey din se Asr ke waqt tak mazdoorii karne par taiyaar ho gaey. phir us shakhs ne kaha ke Asr ki Namaz se suraj doobney tak 2-2 qirat par kon shakhs mera kaam karega? tumhen malum hona chahiye ke wo tumhen ho jo 2-2 qirat ki mazdoorii par Asr se suraj doobney tak kaam karogey. tum aagah raho ke tumhari mazdoorii dugnii hai. yahood w nasara is faisla par ghussa ho gaey aur kehney lagey ke kaam to ham zyada karein aur mazdoorii hamiin ko kam miley. Allah Taala ne unse farmaya kya maine tumhen tumhara haq dene mein koi kami ki hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. Allah Taala ne farmaya ke phir ye mera Fazal hai, main jisey chaahoon zyada dun."
3460,"maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unhon-ne kaha Allah Taala falan ko tabah kare. unhein kya malum nahi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ''yahood par Allah ki laanat ho, unke liye charbi haram hui to unhon-ne usey pighlaa kar bechna shuru kar diya. ''is riwayat ko Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Jaabir aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai."
3461,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meraa paigham logon ko pahunchaao! agarche aik hi aayat ho aur Bani-Israeel ke waaqiaat tum bayan kar saktey ho, unmein koi harj nahi aur jisne mujh par qasdan jhoot baandha to usey apne jahannam ke thikaaney ke liye taiyaar rehna chaahiye.''"
3462,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''yahood w nasara (daadhii wghaira) mein khizaab nahi lagaatey, tum log iske khilaf tariqa ikhtiyar karo (yani khizaab lagaya karo).''"
3463,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf is hadis ki nisbat ghalat ki hogi, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' pichhley zamaney mein aik shakhs (ke hath mein) zakhm ho gaya tha aur usey us se badi takleef thi, aakhir us ne chhuri se apna hath kaat liya iska nateeja ye hua ke khoon bahney laga aur usi se wo mar gaya phir Allah Taala ne farmaya ke mere bandey ne khud mere paas aaney mein jaldi ki isliye maine bhi jannat ko is par haram kar diyaa.''"
3464,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Bani-Israeel mein teen shakhs they, aik kodhii, doosra andha aur tesraa ganjaa. Allah Taala ne chaha ke unka imtihaan ley. chunanche Allah Taala ne unke paas aik farishta bhejaa. farishta pahley kodhii ke paas aaya aur us se puchha ke tumhen sabse zyada kya cheez pasand hai? us ne jawab diya ke achchha rang aur achi chamdii kyonke mujh se log parhez kartey hain. bayan kya ke Farishtey ne is par apna hath phera to uski bimari door ho gaee aur uska rang bhi khoobsurat ho gaya aur chamdii bhi achi ho gaee. Farishtey ne puchha kis tarah ka maal tum zyada pasand karogey? usne kaha ke oont! ya usne gaaey kahii, Ishaq bin-Abdullah ko is silsiley mein shak tha ke kodhii aur ganjey donon mein se aik ne oont ki khahish ki thi aur doosrey ne gaaey ki. chunanche usey haamla ontni di gaee aur kaha gaya ke Allah Taala tumhen ismein barkat dega, phir farishta ganjey ke paas aaya aur us se puchha ke tumhen kya cheez pasand hai? usne kaha ke umda baal aur maujooda aib mera khatm ho jaey kyonke log uski wjah se mujh se parhez kartey hain. bayan kya ke Farishtey ne iske sar par hath phera aur iska aib jata raha aur uske bajaey umda baal aa gaey. Farishtey ne poochha, kis tarah ka maal pasand karogey? usne kaha ke gaaey! bayan kya ke Farishtey ne usey haamla gaaey de di aur kaha ke Allah Taala ismein barkat dega. phir andhey ke paas farishta aaya aur kaha ke tumhen kya cheez pasand hai? usne kaha ke Allah Taala mujhey aankhon ki roshni dedey taake main logon ko dekh sakoon. bayan kya ke Farishtey ne hath phera aur Allah Taala ne uski beenaaii usey wapas de di. phir puchha ke kis tarah ka maal tum pasand karogey? usne kaha ke bakriyaan! Farishtey ne usey haamla bakri de di. phir teenon janwaron ke bachchey paida huey, yahan tak ke kodhii ke oonton se uski wadi bhar gaee, ganjey ki gaaey bail se uski wadi bhar gaee aur andhey ki bakriyon se uski wadi bhar gaee. phir dobara farishta apni usi pehli shakl mein kodhii ke paas aaya aur kaha ke main aik bahut hi zyada miskeen w faqeer aadmi hun, safar ka tamam saman w asbaab khatm ho chuka hai aur Allah Taala ke siwa aur kisi se zarurat poori honey ki ummeed nahi, lekin main tum se usi zaat ka waasta de kar jisne tumhen achchha rang aur achchha chamda aur maal ata kya, aik oont ka sawal karta hun jis se safar ko pura kar sakoon. us ne Farishtey se kaha ke mere zimme huquq aur bahut se hain. farishte ne kaha, ghaaliban main tumhen pehchanta hun, kya tumhen kodh ki bimari nahi thi jiski wjah se log tum se ghin khaatey they. tum aik faqeer aur kangaal they. phir tumhen Allah Taala ne ye cheezein ata kiin? usne kaha ke ye saari daulat to mere bap-dada se chali aa rahi hai. Farishtey ne kaha ke agar tum jhootey ho to Allah tumhen apni pehli haalat par lota de. phir farishta ganjey ke paas apni usi pehli sura mein aaya aur usse bhi wahi darkhaast ki aur us ne bhi wahi kodhii wala jawab diya. Farishtey ne kaha ke agar tum jhootey ho to Allah Taala tumhen apni pehli haalat par lota de. iske baad farishta andhey ke paas aaya, apni usi pehli sura main aur kaha ke main aik miskeen aadmi hun, safar ke tamam saman khatm ho chukey hain aur siwa Allah Taala ke kisi se haajat poori honey ki tawaqqo nahi. main tum se us zaat ka waasta de kar jisne tumhen tumhari beenaaii wapas di hai, aik bakri mangta hun jis se apne safar ki zarooriyaat poori kar sakoon. andhey ne jawab diya ke waqei main andha tha aur Allah Taala ne mujhey apne Fazal se beenaaii ata farmai aur waqei mein faqeer w mohtaaj tha aur Allah Taala ne mujhey maaldaar banaya. tum jitni bakriyan chaho ley saktey ho, Allah ki qism jab tum ne Allah ka waasta diya hai to jitna bhi tumhara ji chahey ley jao, main tumhen hargiz nahi rok sakta. Farishtey ne kaha ke tum apna maal apne paas rakho, ye to sirf imtihaan tha aur Allah Taala tum se razi aur khush hai aur tumharey donon sathiyon se naraz hai."
3465,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''pichhley zamaney mein (banii-Israaeel mein se) teen aadmi kahin rastey mein ja rahe they ke achcha barish ne unhein aa liya. wo teenon pahaad ke aik khooh (ghaar) mein ghus gaey (jab wo andar chaley gaey) to ghaar ka munh band ho gaya. ab teenon aapas mein yun kehney lagey ke Allah ki qism hamein us museebat se ab to sirf sachchai hi nijat dilaaegii. behtar ye hai ke ab har shakhs apne kisi aisey amal ko bayan karke dua karey jiske barey mein usey yaqin ho ke wo khalis Allah Taala ki raza mandi ke liye kya tha. chunanche aik ne is tarah dua ki. aey Allaah! tujh ko khub malum hai ke maine aik mazdoor rakha tha jisne aik farq (teen saa') chaawal ki mazdoorii par mera kaam kya tha lekin wo shakhs (ghusse mein aa kar) chala gaya aur apne chaawal chhod gaya. phir maine us aik farq chaawal ko liya aur uski kheti ki. us se itna kuchh ho gaya ke maine paidawar mein se gaaey bail khareed liye. iske bahut din baad wahi shakhs mujh se apni mazdoorii maangney aaya. maine kaha ke ye gaaey-bail khadey hain unko ley jaa. usne kaha ke mera to sirf aik farq chaawal tum par hona chahiye tha. maine us se kaha ye sab gaaey-bail ley ja kyonke usi aik farq ki aamadni hai. aakhir wo gaaey-bail lekar chala gaya. to aey Allah ! agar to janta hai ke ye emaandari maine sirf terey dar se ki thi to to ghaar ka munh khol de. chunanche usi waqt wo patthar kuchh hat gaya. phir doosrey ne is tarah dua ki. aey Allaah! tujhey khub malum hai ke mere maan-baap jab boodhey ho gaey to main unki khidmat mein rozaana raat main apni bakriyon ka doodh la kar pilaya karta tha. aik din ittifaq se main der se aaya to wo so chukey they. idhar mere biwi aur bachchey bhook se bilbilaa rahe they lekin meri aadat thi ke jab tak waalidain ko doodh na pilaa loon , biwi bachchon ko nahi deta tha mujhey unhein bedaar karna bhi pasand nahi tha aur chhodnaa bhi pasand na tha (kyonke yahi unka Sham ka khana tha aur uske na peeney ki wjah se wo kamzor ho jatey ( isliye main unka wahin intizar karta raha yahan tak ke subah ho gaee. to agar terey ilm mein bhi maine ye kaam terey khof ki wjah se kya tha to to hamari mushkil door kar de. us waqt wo patthar kuchh aur hat gaya aur ab aasman nazar aaney laga. phir teesrey shakhs ne yun dua ki. aey Allah ! meri aik chacha zaad behan thi jo mujhey sabse zyada mahboob thi. maine aik baar us se sohbat karni chaahii, us ne inkar kya magar is shart par taiyaar hui ke main usey so ashrafii la kar de dun. maine ye raqam hasil karne ke liye koshish ki. aakhir wo mujhey mil gaee to main uske paas aaya aur wo raqam uske hawale kar di. usne mujhey apne nafs par qudrat de di. jab main iske donon paon ke darmyan baith chuka to usne kaha ke Allah se dar aur mehar ko baghair haq ke na tod. main (ye suntey hi) khada ho gaya aur so ashrafii bhi wapas nahi li. to agar terey ilm mein bhi maine ye amal terey khof ki wjah se kya tha to, to hamari mushkil aasan kar de. Allah Taala ne unki mushkil door kar di aur wo teenon bahar nikal aaey."
3466,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik aurat apne bachchey ko doodh pilaa rahi thi ke aik sawar udhar se guzraa, wo us waqt bhi bachchey ko doodh pilaa rahi thi (sawaar ki shaan dekh kar) aurat ne dua ki : aey Allah ! mere bachchey ko us waqt tak maut na dena jab tak ke us sawar jaisa na ho jaey. usi waqt (Allah ki qudrat sey) bachcha bol padaa. aey Allah ! mujhey us jaisa na karna aur phir wo doodh peeney laga. iske baad aik aurat ko idhar se ley jaya gaya, usey ley janey waley usey ghaseet rahe they aur uska mazaaq uda rahe they. maan ne dua ki : aey Allah ! mere bachchey ko us aurat jaisa na karnaa, lekin bachchey ne kaha ke aey Allaah! mujhey usi jaisa bana dena ( phir to maan ne poochha, arey ye kya mamla hai? us bachchey ne bataya ke sawar to kaafir w zaalim tha aur aurat ke mutaalliq log kehtey they ke to zina karaatii hai to wo jawab deti (Allah mere liye kafi hai, wo meri paak daamanii janta hai) log kehtey ke to chori karti hai to wo jawab deti ( حسبي الله ( (Allah mere liye kafi hai aur wo meri paak daamanii janta hai)."
3467,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan farmaya ''eik kutta aik kuwein ke charon taraf chakkar kaat raha tha jaisey piyaas ki shiddat se uski jaan nikal janey wali ho ke Bani-Israeel ki aik zaaniya aurat ne usey dekh liya. us aurat ne apna moza utaar kar kuttey ko pani pilaya aur uski maghfirat usi amal ki wjah se ho gaii.''
3468,"aik saal jab wo Haj ke liye gaey huey they, to mimbare-nabawii par khadey ho kar unhon-ne peshani ke baalon ka aik kachchha liya jo unke chaukeedaar ke hath mein tha aur farmaya : aey Madina waalo! tumharey ulma kidhar gaey maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is tarah (baal jodney ki) manaahii farmai thi aur farmaya tha ke Bani-Israeel par barbadi us waqt aai jab (shariiat ke khilaaf) unki aurton ne is tarah baal sanwaarney shuru kar diye they."
3469,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''pichhlii ummaton mein muhaddis log hua kartey they aur agar meri ummat mein koi aisa hai to wo umr bin-Khattab hain.''
3470,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''banii-Israaeel mein aik shakhs tha jisne ninyaanwe khoon nahaq kiye they phir wo naadim ho kar) masla poochhney niklaa. wo aik darwesh ke paas aaya aur us se puchha kya us gunah se tauba qabool honey ki koi sura hai? darwesh ne jawab diya ke nahi. ye sun kar usne us darwesh ko bhi qatl kar diya (aur so khoon poorey kar diye) phir wo (doosron se) poochhney laga. aakhir usko aik darwesh ne bataya ke falan basti mein chala jaa) (wo aadhey rastey bhi nahi pahuncha tha ke) uski maut waaqe ho gaee. martey-martey us ne apna Sina us basti ki taraf jhukaa diya. aakhir rehmat ke farishton aur azab ke farishton mein aapasii jhagdaa hua. (ke kon usey ley jaey) lekin Allah Taala ne us Nasra naam ke basti ko (jahaan wo tauba ke liye ja raha tha) hukm diya ke uski laash se qareeb ho jaey aur dusri basti ko (jahaan se wo nikla tha) hukm diya ke uski laash se door ho jaa. phir Allah Taala ne farishton se farmaya ke ab donon ka fasla dekho aur (jab naapaa to) us basti ko (jahaan wo tauba ke liye ja raha tha) aik baalisht laash se nazdeek paya isliye wo bakhsh diya gaya.
3471,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne subah ki Namaz padhi phir logon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya ''eik shakhs (banii-Israaeel ka ( apni gaaey haankey liye ja raha tha ke wo is par Sawar ho gaya aur phir usey maaraa. us gaaey ne (Allah ki qudrat sey) kaha ke ham janwar sawari ke liye nahi paida kiye gaey. hamari paidaaish to kheti ke liye hui hai.'' logon ne kaha sub'haan-Allaah! gaaey baat karti hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main is baat par eman laataa hun aur Abu-Bakar aur umr bhii. halanke ye donon wahan maujood bhi nahi they. isi tarah aik shakhs apni bakriyan charaa raha tha ke aik bhediyaa aaya aur rewad mein se aik bakri utha kar ley janey laga. rewad wala douda aur usne bakri ko bhediye se chhudaa liya. is par bhediyaa (Allah ki qudrat sey) bola, aaj to tum ne mujh se usey chhudaa liya lekin darindon waley din main (qiyamat ke qareeb) usey kon bachaaeyga jis din mere siwa aur koi iska charwaha na hoga? logon ne kaha, Subhan-Allah ! bhediyaa baatein karta hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main to is baat par eman laya aur Abu-Bakar w umr bhi halanke wo donon us waqt wahan maujood na they. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha aur ham se Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne kaha, ham se Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Misar se, unhon-ne Sad bin Ibrahim se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se riwayat kya aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis bayan ki."
3472,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''eik shakhs ne doosrey shakhs se makan khareedaa aur makan ke khareedaar ko us makan mein aik ghadaa mila jis mein sona tha jis se wo makan us ne khareedaa tha us se usne kaha bhai ghadaa ley jaa. kyonke maine tum se ghar khareedaa hai sona nahi khareedaa tha. lekin pahley Malik ne kaha ke maine ghar ko un tamam chizon samet tumhen bech diya tha jo uske andar maujood hon. ye donon aik teesrey shakhs ke paas apna muqaddima ley gaey. faisla karne waley ne unse puchha kya tumharey koi aulad hai? is par aik ne kaha ke mere aik ladka hai aur doosrey ne kaha ke meri aik ladki hai. faisla karne waley ne unse kaha ke ladkey ka ladki se nikah kar do aur sona unhiin par kharch kar do aur khairat bhi kar do.''
3473,taaoon ke barey mein aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya suna hai? unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke taaoon aik azab hai jo pahley Bani-Israeel ke aik giroh par bheja gaya tha ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke aik pichhli ummat par bheja gaya tha. isliye jab kisi jagah ke mutaalliq tum suno (ke wahan taaoon phaila hua hai) to wahan na jao. lekin agar kisi aisi jagah ye wabaa phail jaey jahan tum pahley se maujood ho to wahan se mat niklo. abu-Nazar ne kaha yani bhaagney ke siwa aur koi gharaz na ho to mat niklo.
3474,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se taaoon ke barey mein puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye aik azab hai, Allah Taala jis par chahta hai bhejta hai lekin Allah Taala ne usko mominon ke liye rehmat bana diya hai. agar kisi shakhs ki basti mein taaoon phail jaey aur wo sabr ke sath Allah ki rehmat se ummeed lagaey huey wahin thehra rahe ke hoga wahi jo Allah Taala ne qismat mein likha hai to usey Shahid ke barabar sawab milega."
3475,"makhzoomiya khatun (Faatima binte- Aswad) jisne (jange-fatah ke mauqe par) chori kar li thi, iske maamle ne Quraish ko fikr mein daal diya. unhon-ne aapas mein mashwara kya ke is maamle par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se guftgu kon karey! aakhir ye tay paya ke Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bahut azeez hain. unke siwa aur koi uski himmat nahi kar sakta. chunanche Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us barey mein kuchh kaha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Usaama! kya to Allah ki hadon mein se aik had ke barey mein mujh se sifarish karta hai? phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur khutba diya (jis mein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, pichhli bahut si ummatein isliye halaak ho gain ke jab unka koi sharif aadmi chori karta to usey chhod detey aur agar koi kamzor chori karta to is par had qaaim kartey aur Allah ki qasam! agar Fatima binte- Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi chori karey to main iska bhi hath kaat daalun."
3476,"maine aik sahabi (Amr-bin-al-Aas) ko Quran Majeed ki aik aayat padhtey suna. wahi aayat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske khilaf qirat ke sath main sun chuka tha, isliye main unhein sath lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye waqia bayan kya lekin maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehre par uski wjah se narazagi ke aasaar dekhey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum donon achchha padhtey ho. aapas mein ikhtilaf na kya karo. tum se pahley log usi qism ke jhagdon se tabah ho gaey."
3477,"Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main maano Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us waqt dekh raha hun. aap Bani-Israeel ke aik Nabi ka waqia bayan kar rahe they ke unki qaum ne unhein maara aur khoon aalud kar diya. lekin wo Nabi khoon saaf kartey jatey aur ye dua kartey ( اللهم اغفر لقومي (ke aey Allaah! meri qaum ki maghfirat farmaa. ye log jantey nahi hain."
3478,"guzishta ummaton mein aik aadmi ko Allah Taala ne khub daulat di thi. jab uski maut ka waqt aaya to usne apne beton se puchha main tumharey haq mein kaisa bap Sabit hua? beton ne kaha ke aap hamarey behtreen bap they. us shakhs ne kaha lekin maine umr bhar koi nek kaam nahi kya. isliye jab main mar jaun to mujhey jalaa daalnaa, phir meri haddiyon ko pees daalnaa aur (raakh ko) kisi sakht aandhii ke din hawa mein uda dena. beton ne aisa hi kya. lekin Allah paak ne usey jama kya aur puchha ke tu ney aisa kyon kya? us shakhs ne arz kya ke parwardigar terey hi khof se chunanche Allah Taala ne usey apne saaya rehmat mein jagah di. is hadis ko Muaz Anbari ne bayan kya ke ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne, unhon-ne Aqba bin abdul-Ghaafir se suna, unhon-ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
3479,ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jo hadisein suni hain wo aap ham se kyon bayan nahi kartey ? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey suna tha ke aik shakhs ki maut ka waqt jab qareeb hua aur wo zindagi se bilkul naa-ummeed ho gaya to apne ghar walon ko wasiiyat ki ke jab meri maut ho jaey to pahley mere liye bahut si lakdiyan jama karna aur us se aag jalaanaa. jab aag mere jism ko khaak bana chukey aur sirf haddiyaan baqi reh jayen to haddiyon ko pees lena aur kisi sakht garmi ke din mein ya (yoon farmaya ke) sakht hawa ke din mujhko hawa mein uda dena. lekin Allah Taala ne usey jama kya aur puchha ke tu ney aisa kyon kya tha? usne kaha ke terey hi dar se. aakhir Allah Taala ne usko bakhsh diya. Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey ye hadis suni hai. ham se Musa ne bayan kya kaha ham se abu-Awana ne bayan kya kaha ham se Abdul-Malik ne bayan kya aur kaha ke is riwayat mein) في يوم راح ( hai) siwa shak ke) iske mana bhi kisi tez hawa ke din ke hain.
3480,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''eik shakhs logon ko qarz diya karta tha aur apne naukaron ko us ne ye keh rakha tha ke jab tum kisi ko muflis paogey (jo mera qarz daar ho ( to usey maaf kar diya karo. mumkin hai Allah Taala bhi hamein maaf farma de.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab wo Allah Taala se mila to Allah ne usey bakhsh diyaa.''
3481,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''eik shakhs bahut gunah kya karta tha jab uski maut ka waqt qareeb aaya to apne beton se usne kaha ke jab main mar jaun to mujhey jalaa daalnaa phir meri haddiyon ko pees kar hawa mein uda dena. Allah ki qasam! agar mere rab ne mujhey pakad liya to mujhey itna sakht azab karega jo pahley kisi ko bhi us ne nahi kya hoga. jab wo mar gaya to (uskii wasiiyat ke mutaabiq) uske sath aisa hi kya gaya. Allah Taala ne zameen ko hukm farmaya ke agar aik zarra bhi kahin uske jism ka terey paas hai to usey jama karke laa. zameen hukm bajaa laai aur wo banda ab (apne rab ke saamney) khada hua tha. Allah Taala ne malum farmaya : tu ney aisa kyon kya? us ne arz kya : aey rab! terey dar ki wjah se. aakhir Allah Taala ne uski maghfirat kar di. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa doosrey sahaba ne is hadis mein lafz ( خشيتك‏ (ke badal ( مخافتك ( kaha hai (donon lafzon ka matlab aik hi hai).
3482,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(banii-Israaeel ki) aik aurat ko aik billi ki wjah se azab diya gaya tha jisey usne qaid kar rakha tha jis se wo billi mar gaee thi aur uski saza mein wo aurat dozakh mein gaee. jab wo aurat billi ko baandhey huey thi to usne usey khaney ke liye koi cheez na di, na peeney ke liye aur na us ne billi ko chhoda hi ke wo zameen ke keedey makodey hi kha letii.''"
3483,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''logon ne agley paighambaron ke kalam jo paaey unmein ye bhi hai ke jab tujh mein haya na ho to phir jo ji chahey kar.''
3484,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agley paighambaron ke kalam mein se logon ne jo paya ye bhi hai ke jab tujh mein haya na ho phir jo ji chahey kar.''
3485,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''eik shakhs takabbur ki wjah se apna tehband zameen se ghaseet'taa hua ja raha tha ke usey zameen mein dhansaa diya aur ab wo qiyamat tak yun hi zameen mein dhanstaa chala jaaeyga.'' Yunus ke sath us hadis ko Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya hai.
3486,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ham (duniyaa mein) tamam ummaton ke aakhir mein aaey lekin (qiyamat ke din) tamam ummaton se aagey hongey. sirf itna farq hai ke unhein pahley kitab di gaee aur hamein baad mein mili aur yahi wo (Jum'a ka ( din hai jiske barey mein logon ne ikhtilaf kya. yahudiyon ne to usey uske doosrey din (hafte ko) kar liya aur nasara ne teesrey din (itwaar ko).''
3487,to har musalman ko haftey mein aik din (yani Juma ke din) to usey jism aur sar ko dho lena lazim hai.
3488,"Muawiya bin abi Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne Madina ke apne aakhiri safar mein hamein Khattab farmaya aur (khutbe ke dauraan) aap ne baalon ka aik guchchaa nikala aur farmaya, mein samajhta hun ke yahudiyon ke siwa aur koi is tarah na karta hoga aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is tarah baal sanwaarney ka naam ( الزور ( (faraib w jhoot) rakha hai. aap ki murad baalon mein jod lagaaney se thi (jaisey aksar auratein banaawtii baalon mein jod kya karti hain) Adam ke sath us hadis ko ghandar ne bhi Shoba se riwayat kya hai."
